quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,Qaaf. (Insiguro y’iyi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwayo n’Imana yonyene gusa). Ndarahiye kuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu
  50,2,"Ahubwo baratangara yuko mwashikiwe n’uwutuza avuye muribo, nabo abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri baca bavuga bati:- iri n’ijambo vy’igitangaza"
  50,3,"Yuko mugihe tuzopfa n’ukuba ivu, ingaruka y’ivyo vyose niya kure cane"
  50,4,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turazi neza urugero rw’ibintu bigabanywa n’Isi hamwe n’ibiri mumibiri y’abo, n’iwacu niho hari igitabu kibitswe mwo ibintu vyose"
  50,5,Mugabo barahakanye ukuri kwama mugihe kwabashikira nabo bari mu bintu vy’imvururu kuribo
  50,6,Mbega ntibabona Amajuru ari hejuru yabo mbega twayubatse gute n’uku yashariza kandi adafise imigaga
  50,7,N’Isi twarayishashe ko n’ukuyishira ko imisozi n’ukuyinagisha ko ibiterwa vyiza vy’ubwoko bwose
  50,8,"Ni\tnugurura\tamaso\tn’icibutso\tc’umuntu\tuwariwe\twese\tazoba yatumbereye"
  50,9,"Twaramanuye\tamazi\tavuye\tmubicu\tahezagiwe\tno\tkuriyo\ttunagisha imirima n’ibitegwa mbumba rugo"
  50,10,"N’ibiti\tvy’imitende\tbirebire\tbiriko\tn’ivyamwa\tvyujuje\tkandi\tbigere keranye bimwe kubindi"
  50,11,"Kugira\tngo\tbibe\tibifungurwa\tvy’abantu\tn’ukuzura\tibisagara\tvyari vyarapfuye, uko rero niko kuzoba ukuzurwa kw’abantu bose"
  50,12,"Barahakanye\tabaho\thambere\tyabo\tmu\tbantu\tbo\tkuntumwa\ty’Imana Nuhu (iii) hamwe n’abahora baba kwa Rassi na Thamudu"
  50,13,N’abo kwa Aadi na Fir’auni hamwe n’abo kwa Lutwi
  50,14,"N’ababa\tmuma\tshamba\tnabo\tkwa\tTubba’a\tabo\tbose\tbarahakanye intumwa z’Imana, kuri ivyo rero ituza ryanje ryaraba shikiye"
  50,15,"Mbega twararushe mu kurema kwacu kwambere, rero bari n’amakenga gusa kw’irema ryacu rishasha"
  50,16,"Ntankeka twaremye ikiremwa muntu natwe tuzi neza ibica k’umutima wiwe, natwe turi hafi cane yiwe gusumba umutsi w’izosi ryiwe"
  50,17,"Mugihe\tbakiriye\tabakira\tuko\tari\tbabiri,\tuwuri\tk’uruhande\trw’iburyo n’uwuri kuruhande rw’ibubanfu"
  50,18,Ntawuvuga ijambo iryariryo ryose atari uko hafi yiwe hari uwurindiriye kwandika gusa
  50,19,"N’ugukura umutima mugihe kuzomu shikira bimwe vy’ukuri, aho niho azobwirwa ati:- ibi n’ivyo bintu wahora uhunga"
  50,20,"Hazovuzwa inzamba, uwo niwo musi w’imperuka"
  50,21,"Hazoshika\tumutima\tw’umwumwe\twese\thamwe\tn’uwuwu\tcungereye hamwe n’icabona ciwe"
  50,22,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\twari\twarasamaye\tn’ibi\tbintu,\trero\tturagukuriye\tko\turu ruzitiro rwawe, n’ukubona kwawe uno musi kubaye ugukaze cane"
  50,23,"Nawa mumarayika bari kumwe nawe azovuga ati:- ibi nivyo vyateguwe kuri jewe"
  50,24,"Nimu\tmujugunyire\tmumuriro\tudahera\twitiriwe\tJahannamu k’umuhakanyi w’Imana yiyonkoye"
  50,25,Uwubuza kugira ineza n’ukurenga imbibe zagenywe n’Imana n’uwahora yitera amakenga kubw’iwe
  50,26,"Uwashizeho iyindi Mana hamwe n’Imana y’ukuri, uyo nimu mujugunyire mu bihano bikaze cane"
  50,27,"Mugenzi wiwe yavuze ati:- ewe Muremyi wacu, sina muzimije kugahato ahubwo niwe wenyene yari mubuzimire bwa kure cane"
  50,28,"Imana\tizo\tvuga\titi:-\tntimugire\tamatati\timbere\tyanje,\tkuko\tndamaze gushira imbere igabisho ryanje"
  50,29,"Ijambo ryanje ntirihindurwa, canke jewe simpemukira abantu banje"
  50,30,"Umusi\ttuzobwira umuriro udahera\twitiriwe\tJahannamu\tduti:-\tmbega wujuje? Nawo uzokwishura uti:- mbega hari abandi bongerezwa mwo"
  50,31,N’Ijuru rizo kwegerezwa hafi kubantu batinya Imana yabo y’ukuri kandi ntirizoba kure y’abo
  50,32,Ibi nivyo mwemerewe k’uwuzo tumbera ku Mana n’ukwirinda
  50,33,N’uwutinya Imana nyene impuhwe zihagije mugihe atayibona hanyuma akaza afise umutima utumbereye ku Mana yiwe
  50,34,"Ni mwinjire mw’Ijuru n’amahoro, uwo niwo musi w’ukwicara yo mu buzima bwanyu bwose"
  50,35,"Muri iryo Juru bazoronkera yo ivyo bipfuza mwo vyose, n’iwacu niho hariho vy’inshi gusumba ivyo"
  50,36,"N’abantu bangahe twahoneje imbere yabo bakaba bari bafise ubushobozi kubasumba, nabo baragenda gendeye mu bihugu vyinshi, mbega hariho ubuhungiro"
  50,37,Mu vy’ukuri kuri rino jambo harimwo icibutso k’uwufise umutima canke k’uwutega amatwi yiwe kandi nawe abe ariho
  50,38,"Twararemye\tAmajuru\tn’Isi\thamwe\tn’ibiri\thagati\ty’avyo\tmu\tmyanya y’imisi itandatu, kandi ntaburuhe twaronse"
  50,39,"Rero niwigumye kuri ibi vyose bavuga, nawe uhayagize Umuremyi wawe n’ukuyihimbaza imbere yuko izuba riseruka n’imbere yuko bugoroba"
  50,40,No mw’Ijoro uyihayagize n’inyuma y’ugushira umutwe wawe hasi
  50,41,Kandi wumvirize umusi azo hamagara uwuhamagara avuye ahantu hafi cane
  50,42,"Umusi\tbazokwumva\takamo\tk’ijwi\try’ukuri,\tuwo\tniwo\tmusi\tw’ukuva muntatemwa zabo"
  50,43,"Ntankeka twebwe turarema n’ukwica, n’ingaruka y’abantu iri iwacu"
  50,44,"Igihe Isi izoba sadukira bayive mwo n’ingoga na n’ingoga, iryo rizoba ari ihwaniro ryoroshe cane kuri twebwe"
  50,45,"Twebwe turafise ubumenyi bwinshi bw’ivyo bavuga, kandi wewe ntujejwe kuba hagarikira, ahubwo n’ubibutse ukoresheje iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu k’uwutinya ituza ryanje"
  51,1,Ndarahiye kumiyaga isanzazwa bimwe bikwiye
  51,2,Yikorera ibintu biremereye cane
  51,3,Ikagenda nayo n’ubwitonzi ntangere
  51,4,Hanyuma ikayagaba nganya kw’itegeko ry’Imana
  51,5,Mu vy’ukuri muvyo mwemerewe ni vy’ukuri
  51,6,Mu vy’ukuri ntankeka impembo yanyu izoboneka
  51,7,Ndarahiye kuri aya majuru afise amashusho meza
  51,8,Yuko mwebwe mufise imvugo idahuje n’iyindi
  51,9,Ahindurwa n’ukuri kuri iyo mvugo agahindurwa
  51,10,Abadukanyi bw’ibintu bazo honywa
  51,11,Abari mubujuju bajuragizwa n’ubwo bujuju
  51,12,"Babaza bati:- ni ryari umusi w’intahe"
  51,13,Uwo musi bazohanirwa bari mu muriro udahera
  51,14,"Ni muhonje ibihano vyanyu, kuko ibi vyose nivyo mwahora muhimiriza"
  51,15,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taba\tgamburukira\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmu mirima myiza hamwe n’amasoko y’amazi y’umusarara"
  51,16,"Bakira ivyo Umuremyi wabo yabahaye, mu vy’ukuri bahora bagira ineza imbere yibi vyose"
  51,17,Bahora baryama itiro rikeyi cane mugihe c’ijoro
  51,18,Basaba imbabazi mugihe c’imbere y’umutwenzi
  51,19,No mu matungo yabo hari ngombwa yuguha umukene asegereza hamwe n’uwigumya mukuda saba
  51,20,No kuri iy’Isi harimwo ibimenyetso kubafise ivyemezo nyakuri
  51,21,"No mumitima yanyu, mbega ntavyo mubona"
  51,22,No mu Majuru hariho imigisha yanyu kandi mwemerewe
  51,23,Rero ndarahiye ku Muremyi w’Ijuru n’Isi yuko mu vy’ukuri ibi vyose ni vy’ukuri nkuko bimeze n’ingene mubivuga
  51,24,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru z’abashitsi b’iteka b’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  51,25,"Mugihe binjira munzu yiwe bavuga bati:- Amahoro y’Imana abe kuri wewe ntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) nawe abishura ati:- Amahoro y’Imana abe kuri mwebwe bashitsi ntamenye"
  51,26,Mukanya aca agenda murugo iwe no kumutambukanyi wiwe arabazimana intama nziza inuze
  51,27,"Arabashikiriza hafi y’abo n’ukuvuga ati:- mbega ko muda fungura"
  51,28,"Aca abagirira ko amakenga, nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntutinye, nabo baca bamushikiriza inkuru nziza z’ikibondo gifise ubumenyi buhagije"
  51,29,"Ninaho umunega w’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) y’aba tumbera nawe avuga yikubita mumaso n’igitangaro cinshi avuga ati:- umukecuru nkanje kandi w’ingumba nzo vyara"
  51,30,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- egome, nuko nyene n’uko Umuremyi wawe yabivuze, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubuhizi ifise n’ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  51,31,"Yavuze ati:- none ivyipfuzo vyanyu n’ibihe mwebwe mwarungitswe"
  51,32,"Nabo bishura bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarungitswe kugira ngo tugende guhonya b’abantu babi"
  51,33,Kugira ngo tubajugunyire ko iminana y’ivyondo vy’umuriro
  51,34,Yashizwe ko ibimenyetso n’Umuremyi wawe kubera abo bantu barenze imbibe z’Imana kubijanye n’ibicumuro vyabo
  51,35,"Kubera ivyo, twakuye mwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bari muri ico gisagara"
  51,36,Mugabo ntitwahasanze muri ico gisagara atari inzu imwe y’aba Isilamu
  51,37,Dusigamwo ikimenyetso kuri bamwe batinya ibihano bibabaza
  51,38,"No\tkunkuru\ty’intumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tigihe\ttwamutwara\tkwa Fir’auni dufise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro"
  51,39,"Mugabo\tyarahakanye\tkubera\tubushobozi\tbwiwe\tn’ukuvuga\tati:-\tuyu muntu n’umurozi canke n’umusazi"
  51,40,"Duca\tturamufata\thamwe\tn’ingabo\tziwe\tn’ukuba\tjugunya\tmukiyaga, kandi nawe atabwa ko n’umwikomo"
  51,41,"No\tkunkuru\ty’intumwa\ty’Imana\tAadi\t(iii)\tmugihe\ttwaba\trungikira umuyaga ukaze cane w’ukubahonya"
  51,42,"Ntiwa\tsigaza\tikintu\ticarico\tcose\tcawushikiye,\tahubwo\tcawugize nk’umugozi uhoyahoya"
  51,43,"N’inkuru\tzabo\tkwa\tThamuda\tmugihe\tbavuga\tbati:-\tni\tmwinezereze kugihe kigufiya gusa"
  51,44,"Barahakana\titegeko\try’Umuremyi\twabo,\tmukanya\tisase\tumucanwa w’inkuba niwo wasokoye imitima yabo nabo bibonera"
  51,45,Nti bashoboye guhagarara canke nti bashoboye kwirwanako
  51,46,"N’abantu\tb’intumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tnabone\timbere\tyabo,\tmu vy’ukuri bari mu bantu b’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  51,47,"N’amajuru twayagize k’ububasha bwacu, mu vy’ukuri ni twebwe bene ubushobozi bw’ibintu vyose"
  51,48,"N’Isi twarayishashe, rero abayishashe neza twebwe turi mu bantu beza gute"
  51,49,Mu vy’ukuri ibintu vyose twabiremye harimwo ikigabo n’ikigore kugira ngo mutegere neza
  51,50,"Rero\tni\tmwirukire\tku\tMana,\tjewe\tkuri\tmwebwe\tndi\tuwutuza k’umugaragaro mvuye iwe"
  51,51,"Kandi ntimugire uwundi kuba ariwe asengwa hamwe n’Imana, ntankeka jewe ndi mubatuza mboneka neza kuri mwebwe, kandi mvuye iwe"
  51,52,"Nuko rero nta ntumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose yashikiye abamyeho imbere yabo atari uko bavuga bati:- uyu n’umurozi canke n’umusazi"
  51,53,Mbega harico bapfana nibi bintu? Mugabo n’abantu babi cane
  51,54,"Ntaco ni mubareke gutyo nyene, na wewe ntuzo tabwako umwikomo"
  51,55,"N’ubandanye\tubibutsa,\tkuko\tuko\tkwibutsa\tkwawe\tniko\tkuzofasha abemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  51,56,Sinaremye ibisigo n’abantu mugabo n’uko bonsega
  51,57,"Sinkeneye kuribo imigisha iyariyo yose, canke\tsinkeneye kuribo yuko bondisha"
  51,58,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tImana\tniyo\tmutanzi\tw’imigisha,\tkandi\tniyo\tnyene ubushobozi bukwiye"
  51,59,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo bazoba bafise ahandi hantu nkaha bagenzi babo bari, rero ntiba ntware gihuti huti"
  51,60,"Ibihano\tbikaze\tcane\tbizoshikira\tbamwe\tbahakana\tumusi\twabo bemerewe"
  52,1,Ndarahiye k’Umusozi
  52,2,No kugitabu canditswe ko ivyo Imama ishaka kwandia
  52,3,K’urupapuro rw’urushato rwiza ruzinguruwe rusomwa
  52,4,No kunyubakwa igenderwa ko imisi yose
  52,5,No k’urusenge rw’amajuru rwareruwe hejuru
  52,6,No kubiyaga vyujujwe mwo amazi
  52,7,Mu vy’ukuri ibihano vy’Umuremyi wawe bizoba ho
  52,8,Ntawuzo bizitira
  52,9,Umusi amajuru azonyiganga ku kunyiganzwa gukomeye cane
  52,10,N’imisozi nayo isenyurwa ibe igendera mukirere k’urugendo runiniya
  52,11,Rero ibihano kuri uwo musi bizoshikira abahakanyi b’Imana
  52,12,N’abafyinata kubintu ata kamaro bifise
  52,13,"Umusi\tbazosunikwa\tmu\tmuriro\tudahera\twitiriwe\tJahannamu k’umusuniko w’inguvu"
  52,14,Uwo niwa mukomezwa mwahora muhakana
  52,15,Mbega ubu n’uburozi canke mwebwe ntimubona
  52,16,"Ni muwinjiremwo uwo muriro udahera murinda canke mutarinda, vyose ni kimwe kuri mwebwe, kuko murihwa kuvyo mwahora mukora"
  52,17,Mu vy’ukuri aba gamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri bazoba bari mumirima n’imigisha myiza
  52,18,"Banezerezwa n’ivyo Umuremyi wabo yabahaye, n’Umuremyi wabo yarabakingiye n’ibihano vy’umuriro udahera waka cane"
  52,19,Ni mufungure kandi munywe n’umunezero ntangere kuvyo mwahora mugira
  52,20,"Bazoba begamiye ku nyegamo z’iteka zatondeshejwe kumirongo, hanyuma tubahe n’abagore beza beza basharije bafise amaso manini maniniya"
  52,21,"Na bamwe bemeye Imana yabo bimwe biboneka baga kurikirwa n’urunganwe rw’ibibondo vyabo n’ukwemera kwabo, abo bantu tuzoba huza nabo bagenzi b’abo, kandi ntituzoba gunga ku bikorwa vyabo, umwe wese azorihwa kuvyo yimbuye"
  52,22,Tuzobaha ivyamwa hamwe n’Inyama nk’uko bavyipfuza
  52,23,"Bazo\thanahana\tibirahuri\tvyujujwe\tmwo\tibinyobwa\tbitazana\tmwo amajambo ataco amaze, canke arimwo ibicumuro"
  52,24,"Hazocamwo\tabakozi\tbabo\tbabereye\tnkuko\twomenga\tn’ubutare bw’umwakaka"
  52,25,Bazorabana bamwe kubandi babazanya
  52,26,"Bavuga bati:- kera twari kumwe n’abantu bacu dutinya Imana yacu"
  52,27,Imana nayo yaratugiriye imbabazi n’ukuturokora n’ibihano vy’umuyaga w’umuriro udahera
  52,28,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe aho hambere twarasenga Imana yonyene rudende, mu vy’ukuri niyo nyene imbabazi n’Impuhwe zihagije"
  52,29,"Rero n’ubandanye ubibutsa\tkubera imigisha yUmuremyi wawe, nturi umurozi kandi nturi umusazi"
  52,30,"Egome\tbaravuga\tyuko\tari\tumwanditsi\tw’amajambo\ty’ubuhizi\tgusa, natwe tumurabira yuko ashikirwa n’urupfu"
  52,31,"Vuga uti:- ni murindire nanje ndi kumwe namwe mu bantu barindiriye"
  52,32,"Canke\tubwo\tbwenge\tbwabo\tbuhanitse\tnibwo\tbubategeka\tibi\tvyose, canke nibo bantu b’amanyama gusa"
  52,33,"Canke\tnibo\tbavuga\tyuko\tiyi\tQur’ani\tariwe\tyayi\tyandikiye\tkubwiwe, ahubwo nta na kimwe bemera"
  52,34,Rero ni bazane ibiganiro nk’ibi niba bavugisha ukuri
  52,35,"Mbega baremwe ata kintu kiriho, canke nibo biremye"
  52,36,"Canke\tnibo\tbaremye\tAmajuru\tn’Isi?\tAhubwo\tntavyemezo\tbafise bw’ikintu na kimwe"
  52,37,"Canke barafise ububiko bw’Umuremyi wawe, canke nibo bene gucisha aho bashaka kumategeko yabo"
  52,38,"Canke barafise idugiro badugira ko ry’ukumviriza ibivugirwa yo, wewe ubumviriza n’uzane ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro"
  52,39,"Canke\tirafise\tibibondo\tvy’abakobwa,\tnamwe\tmurafise\tibibondo vy’abahungu"
  52,40,"Canke\turabasaba\timpembo\tkuri\tivyo\tbaremerewe\tko\thamwe n’amagarama yayo"
  52,41,Canke iwabo barafise ubumenyi butazwi banditse
  52,42,"Canke bagomba bagire amarorerwa, mugabo abahakanye Imana y’abo y’ukuri nibo bazofatwa"
  52,43,Canke iwabo hariho uwundi Muremyi atari Imana? Imana irisukuye nabo bayigereranya nayo
  52,44,"Naho bari kubona ikintu kivuye k’uruhande rwo mw’Ijuru gikorotse hasi bari kuvuga bati:- ibi n’ibicu bigerekeranye kubindi"
  52,45,"Rero n’ubareke kugeza naho bazokorana, n’umusi waho imitima yabo izo sokorwa"
  52,46,N’umusi waho ingeso zabo ataco zizoba marira n’ikintu na gitoyi kandi batazo rokorwa
  52,47,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo bazoba bafise ibindi bihano, mugabo benshi muribo ntana kimwe bazi"
  52,48,"N’urIndire intahe y’Umuremyi wawe, mu vy’ukuri wewe uri imbere y’amaso yacu, kandi n’utakambire Umuremyi wawe gusa kandi uyihayagize mugihe uhagaze uriko urasenga ibisabisho vyose"
  52,49,No hagati mw’ijoro nahone n’uyitakambire n’igihe inyenyeri ziserutse
  53,1,Ndarahiye k’unyenyeri zikorotse
  53,2,Yuko umuntu wanyu atazimiye canke atakosheje
  53,3,Kandi ntavuga amajambo k’ugushaka kwiwe
  53,4,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose avuga atari uko ari ubutumwa bw’Imana yahawe
  53,5,Yaramwigishije uwufise inguvu nyinshi cane
  53,6,Uwufise ububasha nawe afise uburinganire bukwiye
  53,7,Nawe akaba ari mukirere c’ukubona ibiri hejuru cane
  53,8,Hanyuma aregera n’ukumanuka
  53,9,Guca kuba ubube bw’abo bwo hafi nk’umuheto n ’uwundi biri hafi cane
  53,10,Ica imwereka uyo mukozi wiwe kuvyo yeretswe
  53,11,Umutima ntiwabeshe kuvyo wabonye
  53,12,Mbega muharira nawe kubintu yibonera
  53,13,Yaramubonye ubugira kabiri kw’imanuka ryiwe
  53,14,Kugiti c’amaherezo ryayo kiriho
  53,15,Hafi yaho niho hari uwo murima uzovyagira mwo abantu beranda
  53,16,Mugihe capfuka ico giti nica gipfuse
  53,17,Ijisho naryo ntirya buragijwe canke ntiryarenze akarimbi
  53,18,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tyarabonye\tibintu\tbikuru\tbikuru\tmu\tbimenyetso vy’Umuremyi wiwe"
  53,19,Mbega mwarabonye uwitwa Laata hamwe na Uzzaa
  53,20,Hamwe n’uwitwa Manaata agira gatatu
  53,21,"Mbega\tmwebwe\tmurafise\tibibondo\tvy’abahungu\tnayo\tikaba\tifise ibibondo vy’abakobwa"
  53,22,Iryo n’igabanganywa ry’ubuhemu gusa
  53,23,"Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari amazina gusa mwabahaye mwebwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banyu, Imana rero ntiyamanuye ibimenyetso kuri ivyo kuko badakurikiza atari ivyo bikeka ko nivyo imitima yabo yipfuza, mu vy’ukuri uburokoke bwabashikiye buvuye kumuremyi wabo"
  53,24,Mbega umuntu yoshobora kuronka ico yipfuza cose
  53,25,Ni ivy’Imana gusa haba k’umusi w’imperuka no kw’Isi
  53,26,"Hariho Abamarayika bangahe mw’ijuru, ubusabizi bwabo butazo fasha atari munyuma yaho Imana izotanga uruhusha kuwo yishakiye nuku mwemerera"
  53,27,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batemera umusi w’imperukara bahamagara Abamarayika ku mazina y’abakenyezi
  53,28,"Nabo ntabumenyi bafise kuri ivyo, kuko bada kurikiza atari ukwikekeranya gusa, mu vy’ukuri ukwikeka ntigufasha ikintu na kimwe imbere y’ukuri"
  53,29,Rero ni wirinde na bamwe baha ibitugu vyabo iki cibutso cacu kandi ntibashaka atari ubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi gusa
  53,30,"Aya niyo maherezo yabo mu kumenya kwabo, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’umuntu yazimiye munzira yiwe kandi niyo ifise n’ubumenyi bw’uwarokotse"
  53,31,"Ni vy’Imana ibiri mumajuru hamwe n’ibiri kw’Isi kugira ngo ibahembe abantu babi kumabi yabo yose bagira, n’uguhemba ineza kubantu bagira ineza"
  53,32,"Abatitaho ku bicumuro bikuru bikuru hamwe n’ibikorwa vy’umwanda, dukuye mwo amakosa mato mato, ntankeka Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ikigongwe cinshi, kandi niyo ibazi cane kuva akibarema kuri iy’Isi, no kuva mukiri imbanyi z’abavyeyi banyu, rero ntimusukure imitima yanyu, kuko niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije bw’uwisukuye"
  53,33,Mbega wabonye umwe yahindukira
  53,34,Akaba yatanze bikeyi n’uguca yigumya
  53,35,Mbega arafise ubumenyi bw’ibitaboneka n’ukubibona
  53,36,Canke ntiyabwiwe ibiri mu bitabu vy’’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)
  53,37,Hamwe n’ibitabu vy’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yakwijije indagano y’Imana
  53,38,Yuko itakira umutima w’ibicumuro vy’uwundi mutima
  53,39,N’umuntu ntazoronka icarico cose atari kukintu yakoze
  53,40,N’ibikorwa vyiwe yagize bizo bonekana
  53,41,Hanyuma azohembwa impembo yiwe ikwiye
  53,42,Impera n’imperuka n’ugusubira k’Umuremyi wawe
  53,43,Nayo Imana niyo izana ibintu binezereza n’ibitera agahinda
  53,44,Kandi niyo yica n’ukuzura
  53,45,Kandi niyo yaremye ibintu bibiri ikigabo n’ikigore mubintu vyose
  53,46,Mu mbuto z’uruvyaro mugihe zisukiwe mugitereko c’uruvyaro
  53,47,Kandi n’uko hejuru yayo hariho irindi zurwa ry’abantu
  53,48,Kandi kuriyo niyo itanga ibikwiye ni vy’umusesekara
  53,49,Kandi niwe Muremyi w’Inyenyeri yitiriwe Shi’ira
  53,50,Kandi niyo yahoneje Aadi wambere
  53,51,NaThamuda ntihasigaje n’umwe
  53,52,"N’imbere\ty’abo\tabantu\tbo\tkuntumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tnabone barahemukiye imitima yabo gusumba ayandi mabi cane"
  53,53,N’ibisagara vyacuranguwe ikaba ariyo yabi curanguye
  53,54,Irabipfuka ivyapfutswe
  53,55,N’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wawe uyigirira ko amakenga
  53,56,Uyu n’uwutuza mubatuza bakera
  53,57,Icaduka kiri hafi kiregereje
  53,58,Ntawushobora kugikura ho atari Imana yonyene
  53,59,Mbega mutangazwa n’ibi biganiro
  53,60,"N’ugutwenga, kandi mutarira"
  53,61,Murasamaye gusa
  53,62,Rero nimu pfukamire Imana kandi muyisenge
  54,1,"Umwanya wageze, n’Ukwezi kwamanyutse"
  54,2,"Nibabona igitangaro baca bahindukira k’urundi ruhande n’ukuvuga bati:- ubu n’uburozi bwiwe buguma bubandanya"
  54,3,"Barahakanye ibi vyose baca bakurikira ivyo imitima yabo yipfuza, n’ibintu vyose vy’Imana n’ibibaho"
  54,4,Mu vy’ukuri mwarashikiwe n’inkuru zibuza ibintu bikuru bikuru
  54,5,Ubuhizi bukwiye mugabo ituza kuribo ntaco rimaze
  54,6,"Rero ni wirinde nabo, n’umusi azo hamagara uwuzo hamagara kukintu gihambaye cane"
  54,7,"Amaso yabo azoba yunamye hasi, bavuye muntatemwa zabo nka kumwe kw’inzige zasanzajwe"
  54,8,"Birukira kuri uwo atuza mugihe bavuga abo batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- uwu musi uragoye cane"
  54,9,"Imbere yabo, abantu bo kuntumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) nabone barahakanye bararengwa, mugu hakana intumwa yacu baca bavuga yuko ari umusazi hamwe n’ukubwirwa amajambo akomakomeye"
  54,10,"Niho yatakambira Umuremyi wiwe avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nananiwe ahubwo n’undokore"
  54,11,Mumwanya turugurura imiryango y’amajuru n’amazi ashunguruka n’inguvu nyinshi cane
  54,12,"Duca duserura amazi y’amasoko ngaha kw’Isi, n’amazi arahura ku kintu camaze gutegurwa n’Imana"
  54,13,"Duca\tdutwara\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tmu\tbwato\tbwakozwe mumbaho n’imisumari"
  54,14,"Bukaba\tbwagendera\timbere\ty’amaso\tyacu,\tiyi\tn’ingabirano\tku\twari yaranswe"
  54,15,"Mu vy’ukuri twabusize gutyo nk’ikimenyetso, mugabo hariho uwibuka"
  54,16,Mbega ibihano vyanje vyari bimeze gute hamwe n’ugutuza kwanje
  54,17,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\ttwagize\tiyi\tQur’ani\tntagatifu\tngo\tiborohere n’ugutegera kuriyo, mbega hariho uwibuka"
  54,18,"Barahakanye abo kwa Aadi, mbega ibihano vyanje vyari bimeze gute hamwe n’ugutuza kwanje"
  54,19,Mu vy’ukuri twaraba rungikiye Umuyaga w’igihuhusi k’umusi w’umwaku wagumye ubandanya kuribo kugeza uno musi
  54,20,"Uwo\tmuyaga\twarandura\tabantu\tnkakumwe\tbaranduye\tibishitsi vy’imitende vyaranduwe"
  54,21,Mbega ibihano vyanje vyari bimeze gute hamwe n’ugutuza kwanje
  54,22,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\ttwagize\tiyi\tQur’ani\tntagatifu\tngo\tiborohere n’ugutegera kuriyo, mbega hari n’umwe yibuka"
  54,23,Bene Thamudu nabone barahakanye ababa tuza
  54,24,"Bavuze\tbati:-\tyoh!\ttumukurikire\tumuntu\tumwe\tmuri\ttwebwe,\tmu vy’ukuri tuzoba turi mubazimiye kandi turwaye mumitwe yacu twese"
  54,25,"Oya! mbega niwe yamanuriwe gusa icibutso hagati yacu twese, canke niwe mubeshi yibona"
  54,26,Ejo niho bazomenya uwuhe mubeshi yibona
  54,27,"Tuzobazanira\tIngamiya\ty’inyana\tkugira\tngo\ttubagerageze\tgusa,\trero wewe n’ubarabe gusa hanyuma wigumye"
  54,28,"Hanyuma ubamenyeshe yuko amazi azogaburwa hagati yabo, uruhande rumwe rw’amazi ruzoba rufise umuhagaritsi wayo"
  54,29,"Rero\tbarahamagara\tumugenzi\twabo,\taca\tafata\timbugita\tabaga\tya ngamiya barayifungura"
  54,30,Mbega ibihano vyanje vyari bimeze gute hamwe n’ugutuza kwanje
  54,31,"Mu vy’ukuri twaraba rungikiye isumo rimwe gusa, baca baba nk’imizira y’uwubaka urugo rw’imizira rusenyagurika"
  54,32,"Ntankeka\ttwagize\tiyi\tQur’ani\tntagatifu\tngo\tiborohere\tn’ugutegera kuriyo, mbega hari n’umwe yibuka"
  54,33,N’abantu bo kwa Lutwi nabone barahakanye ababatuza
  54,34,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twabarungikiye iminana dukuye mwo abakurikiye intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) nibo twarokoye mubucagu cagu
  54,35,"Kumihezagiro ivuye iwacu, uko niko duhemba abashima"
  54,36,"Mu vy’ukuri niwe yabateye ubwoba bw’ibihano vyacu, mugabo kuribo vyarabateye amakenga muvyo twabatujije"
  54,37,"Bamusavye yuko yobaha abashitsi biwe, natwe duca duhumisha amaso yabo, n’ukuba bwira duti:- ni muhonje ibihano vyanje hamwe n’ituza ryanje"
  54,38,Bazindukiwe mugihe co mugitondo n’ibihano vyabandanije kuribo
  54,39,"Tubabwira duti:- ni muhonje ibihano vyanje, hamwe n’ituza ryanje"
  54,40,"Ntankeka\ttwebwe\ttwagize\tiyi\tQur’ani\tntagatifu\tngo\tiborohere n’ugutegera kuriyo, mbega hari n’umwe yibuka"
  54,41,N’abatuza barashikiwe n’abantu bo kwa Fir’auni nawe nyene arimwo
  54,42,"Barahakana\tivyemezo\tvyacu\tvyose,\tkuri\tivyo\ttwaraba\ttoteje\tnkuko itoteza nyene inguvu n’ubushobozi"
  54,43,Mbega abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri banyu nibo beranda gusumba abo? canke biranditswe mu bitabu yuko mwebwe muzosirwa
  54,44,"Canke\tnibo\tbavuga\tyuko\ttwebwe\tturi\tbenshi\tkandi\ttwishoboje\tmu kwikingira"
  54,45,"Ubwo bwinshi bwabo ubu vuba buzo gendeshwa ningoga\tna ningoga hanyuma bahindure imigongo yabo birukanga"
  54,46,"Mugabo uwo musi w’imperuka niwo mwanya wabo, no kuri iyo saha izoba igoye cane kandi ibabaza cane"
  54,47,Ntankeka izi nkozi z’ikibi bari mu buzimire n’ubusazi
  54,48,"Umusi\tbazo kwegwa bajanwa mu muriro udahera bubitse inda zabo hasi babwirwa bati:- ni muhonje agace gatoyi k’umuriro udahera"
  54,49,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaremye ibintu vyose kurugero rukwiye
  54,50,Ntategeko ryariho atari uko ryari rimwe gusa nk’ugukubita urugohe rumwe gusa
  54,51,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwaramaze\tguhonya\tbagenzi\tbanyu,\tmugabo\tharimwo abibuka"
  54,52,N’ijambo iryariryo ryose bagize riri mu bitabu vyacu
  54,53,N’ikintu gitoyi canke kininiya vyose biranditswe
  54,54,Ntankeka aba gamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri bazoba bari mumirima n’imyonga
  54,55,"Mu\tbwicaro\tbwiza\tburi\tmw’Ijuru\try’Imana,\tUmwami\tw’ubushobozi bw’ibintu vyose"
  55,1,Nyene Imigisha myinshi
  55,2,Yigishije iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu
  55,3,Yaremye ikiremwa muntu
  55,4,Nuku mwigisha kuvuga
  55,5,Izuba n’Ukwezi bigira kugiharuro cayo
  55,6,N’ibiti bito bito na bininiya vyose bigamburukira Imana
  55,7,"N’Amajuru\tyose\tniyo\tyayadugije\thejuru\tn’ukuzishira\tk’uburinganire bungana"
  55,8,Kugira ngo ntimuhemuke mu gupima ku minzani yanyu
  55,9,Rero ni mupime kubipimo vy’ukuri kandi ntimu gabanye kuri iyo minzani
  55,10,N’Isi yayishize ho kubera ibiremwa vyiwe
  55,11,Muriyo harimwo ivyamwa hamwe n’imitende yegeranye kuyindi
  55,12,Harimwo n’ibifungurwa vy’intete bifise ibishishwa hamwe n’ibifungurwa bifise akamoto keza
  55,13,"Mwebwe\tbiremwa\tbantu\tbo\tmubwoko\tbubiri,\tni\tiyihe\tmigisha y’Umuremyi wanyu muhakana"
  55,14,Yaremye umuntu imukuye mw’ivu ry’ibumba nkakumwe kw’ibikoresho ry’ibumba
  55,15,Arema ibisigo akoresheje ururimi rw’umuriro
  55,16,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,17,"Umuremyi\tw’useruko\tbubiri\tn’Umuremyi\tw’uburengera\tzuba\tuko\tari bubiri"
  55,18,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,19,Niyo yahujije ibiyaga bibiri
  55,20,Hagati y’avyo hariho uruzitiro rutinjirana n’ayandi mazi
  55,21,None n’iyihe migisha y’umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,22,Muri ivyo biyaga uko ari bibiri harimwo ibisharizo vyiza vyitiriwe Ilulu hamwe n’ibindi vyitiriwe Mar’jani
  55,23,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,24,"Vyose biri kw’itegeko ryayo kuri ibi vyakozwe bigira\tmubiyaga umengo n’imisozi"
  55,25,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,26,N’ibiri hejuru y’Isi hamwe n’Amajuru vyose bizo zimangana
  55,27,"Hasigare ukwamaho kw’Umuremyi wawe, nyene iteka, n’urupfasoni"
  55,28,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,29,"Bimusaba ibiri mu majuru no kw’Isi ibirimwo vyose n’imisi yose, nayo ikaba iri mubindi bintu"
  55,30,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,31,Ubu vuba tuzoba kurikirana mwebwe ngabo uko muri babiri
  55,32,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,33,"Mwebwe miryango y’ibisigo n’abantu, nimwa shobora kwinyuvya ngo mwinjire mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi, rero ni mwinyuvye, mugabo ntimuzo kwinyuvya atari kububasha bwanje"
  55,34,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
