  55,68,"Harimwo ibiti vy’ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose, cane cane ibiti vy’imitende hamwe n’imikoma manga"
  55,69,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,70,Harimwo n’abapfasoni beza beza
  55,71,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,72,"Bafise amaso yera derere kandi meza manini maniniya kubaguma\tbari mu mazu y’abo gusa"
  55,73,None n’iyihe migisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mwebwe muhakana
  55,74,Abo bapfasoni nti barakorwako n’umuntu uwariwe wese imbere y’abo canke ibisigo
