  55,78,"Rira\tninahajwe\tizina\rry’Umuremyi\rwawe,\rnyene\riteka\tn’urupfasoni\rruyikwiye"
  56,1,Nihaboneka ikizoboneka
  56,2,Ukuboneka kwaco s’ikinyoma
  56,3,Kizo tetereza abantu babi n’uguha iteka abantu beza
  56,4,"Mugi he Isi izo nyiganzwa, ikazo nyiganzwa bimwe vy’inguvu"
  56,5,N’imisozi igihe izo vungagurwa
  56,6,Ibe nk’inkungugu zitumuka
  56,7,Namwe muzoba muri mumice itatu
  56,8,Abantu bagira ineza bazoba bameze gute? Abo bantu bagira ineza
  56,9,N’abantu bagira ishari bazoba bameze gute? Abo bantu bagira ishari
  56,10,"N’abazoba\tbari\timbere\ty’abandi\tmu\tbagira\tineza\tnibo\tbazoba\tbari imbere y’abandi"
  56,11,Abo nibo bazohabwa ikaze n’Imana yabo
  56,12,Mu mirima izoba irimwo imigisha myiza ntangere
  56,13,Ahantu haniniya muri aba ni mubantu bambere
  56,14,N’uruhande rutoyi ni mubantu banyuma
  56,15,Bazoba bari hejuru y’inyegamo z’iteka zisharijwe neza
  56,16,Bazoba bazegamiye ko kandi barabana
  56,17,Babe bakikujwe n’imiyabaga igifise n’amashusho y’ubuyabaga akiri meza abereye kandi ateye igomwe
  56,18,"N’ibikombe\thamwe\tn’amabirika\tn’ibirahuri\tvy’ubunywero\tbivuye\tmu nzuzi aboneka mwo inzira yayo mazi"
  56,19,"Ntibazo meneka imitwe yabo kubera ivyo binyobwa, canke ngo batakaze ubwenge bwabo"
  56,20,N’ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose nkuko bavyipfuza
  56,21,N’inyama z’inyoni nkuko bavyifuza bonyene
  56,22,N’abapfasoni bafise amaso meza kandi manini maniniya
  56,23,Nk’ubutare bwitiriwe Ilulu bunyegejwe
  56,24,N’impembo y’ivyo vyose bahora bagira
  56,25,Muriyo ntibazo kwumva amajambo ataco abamariye canke amajambo y’ibicumuro
  56,26,Atari amajambo y’amahoro n’ayandi gusa
  56,27,"N’aba\tbantu\tb’amahoro\tnabo\tbazoba\tbameze\tgute?\tabo\tbantu b’amahoro"
  56,28,Bazoba bari munsi y’ibitutu vy’ibiti bidafise amahwa
  56,29,N’ingundu z’ibitoki bitondeshejwe neza hamwe n’imivyaro yazo myiza
  56,30,No mu bitutu bigororotse kumpande zose
  56,31,N’amazi ashunguruka neza
  56,32,N’ivyamwa vyinshi vy’ubwoko bwose
  56,33,Ntakama ayo mazi kandi ntabuzwa
  56,34,N’ubusaswa bwabo buri hejuru
  56,35,Twebwe twabaremye mw’ishusho ryiza cane
  56,36,Tuzobagira amasugi nkuko aribwo bwambere bubaka izabo
  56,37,Bakundana n’abacance b’abo
  56,38,Kubera abantu bagira ineza
  56,39,Uruhande runiniya muribo nu rw’abantu baho hambere
  56,40,N’urundi ruhande runiniya nurw’abantu banyuma
  56,41,N’abantu b’ishari bazoba gute abo bantu b’ishari
  56,42,Bazoba bari mu muyaga w’umuriro n’amazi abira nk’amarike
  56,43,N’igitutu c’umwotsi wirabura cane
  56,44,Sicu kuzana akayaga gakanye canke icu kuruhukira mwo
  56,45,"Ntankeka\tbo\tbari\timbere\ty’ibi\tvyose\tbibereye\tmu\tbuzima bw’amahirwe"
  56,46,Bamye bafatiriye ku bicumuro bininiya
  56,47,"Bamye\tbavuga\tbati:-\tnitwapfa\ttukaba\tivu\tn’amagufa\tmasa\tniho tuzozurwa"
  56,48,Canke abavyeyi bacu bakera
  56,49,"Vuga uti:- ntankeka abambere n’abanyuma"
  56,50,Bazo kwegeranywa bose kumwanya wategekanijwe no k’umusi uzwi
  56,51,"Hanyuma\tmwebwe\tmwazimiye\tn’uguhakana\tImana\tyanyu\ty’ukuri"
  56,52,Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muzofungura kugiti citiriwe Zaqqumum
  56,53,Kuri ico giti muzo kwuzuriza mwo inda zanyu
  56,54,No hejuru y’ayo muzonywa amazi ashushe y’amarike
  56,55,"Kandi\tmuzonywa\tnkakumwe\tkw’ingamiya\tziyanywa zifise\tinyota\tya cane"
  56,56,Iyo niyo nzimano yabo yuwo musi w’impembo
  56,57,Ni twebwe twabaremye mugabo ntimutwemera
  56,58,Mbega murabona intanga muteragira
  56,59,Mbega ni mwebwe muzi rema canke ni twebwe tuzirema
  56,60,"Twebwe twabateguriye urupfu, rero ntituzonanirwa n’ukubazura"
  56,61,"Ntituzonanirwa\tkuzana\tabandi\tbantu\tatari\tmwebwe\tn’ukuba\trema murindi shusho mutazi"
  56,62,"Ntankeka mwebwe murafise ubumenyi bw’iremwa ryambere, none ni kuki mutibuka"
  56,63,Mbega murabona ibiterwa mutera
  56,64,Mbega ni mwebwe mubinagisha canke ni twebwe tubinagisha
  56,65,"Iyo dushaka twari kubagira abadafise ubwenge, mukaguma mwidoga gusa"
  56,66,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarigoreye ubusa
  56,67,Ahubwo twebwe twarahakaniwe
  56,68,Mbega murabona amazi munywa
  56,69,Mbega ni mwebwe mwayamanuye muyakuye mubicu canke ni twebwe tuyamanura
  56,70,"Iyo\tdushaka\ttwari\tkuyagira\tay’umunyu\tukaze\tcane,\tnone\tni\tkuki mudashima"
  56,71,Mbega mwebwe murawubona umuriro mwatsa
  56,72,"Mbega\tigiti\tcawo\tni\tmwebwe\tmwakiremye\tcanke\tni\ttwebwe twakiremye"
  56,73,Twebwe twagize ico giti kuba nk’icibutso n’akamaro ku bantu bose
  56,74,Rero ninahaza izina ry’Umuremyi wawe mukuru
  56,75,Rero ndarahiye kw’iseruka ry’Inyenyeri
  56,76,Mu vy’ukuri iyo ntankeka n’indahiro niniya iyo mubi menya
  56,77,Ntankeka iki n’igitabu cegeranye ibikenewe vyose kandi gifise iteka n’icubahiro
  56,78,Icavuye muri ico gitabu kiziganijwe neza cane
  56,79,Nta muntu agikora ko atari mu bantu bisukuye n’amabi yose
  56,80,N’imanuka ry’aco ryavuye ku Muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  56,81,Mbega murakengera ibi biganiro
  56,82,Kandi mukagira imigisha yanyu muyi kengera namwe muyi hakana
  56,83,Mbega igihe umutima w’umuntu uzoba washitse mu muhogo
  56,84,Namwe muri ico gihe muraba
  56,85,Natwe twegeranye nawe cane gusumba mwebwe namwe mutabona
  56,86,"Nk’uko mwebwe mutari\tk’ubutegetsi bwanje"
  56,87,None ni kuki mutosubiza uwo mutima nimwaba mu vugisha ukuri
  56,88,Niyaba ari muri bamwe bahawe ikaze n’Imana
  56,89,N’akanyamuneza ntangere hamwe n’akamoto keza hamwe n’imirima irimwo imigisha myiza ibarorereye
  56,90,Niyaba ari mu bantu beza b’intungane
  56,91,"Rero izobabwirwa iti:- n’amahoro y’Imana kuri wewe, kuko uri mu bantu b’intungane"
  56,92,"Niyaba yari mu bantu b’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, kandi bazimiye"
  56,93,Inzimano yiwe n’amazi ashushe y’amarike
  56,94,N’uguhira mu muriro udahera
  56,95,Ntankeka uku niko kuri nyakuri
  56,96,Rero n’uninahaze izina ry’Umuremyi wawe nyene iteka rikuru
  57,1,"Ibiri mu majuru no kw’Isi vyose bininahaza Imana, kuko niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  57,2,"Ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi vyose ni rwiwe, kuko niyo irema n’ukwica, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  57,3,"Niyo nyene intango kandi niyo nyene iherezo, kandi niyo iboneka nu w’amabanga kandi niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  57,4,"Niyo yaremye Amajuru hamwe n’Isi mumyanya itandatu, hanyuma ivyagira mu bwami bwayo, rero niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyinjira ngaha kw’Isi n’ibisohoka muriyo, hamwe n’ibimanuka bivuye mw’Ijuru n’ibiduga muriyo, nayo iri kumwe namwe aho muherereye hose, kandi niyo ibona ivyo mugira vyose"
  57,5,"Ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi ni rwiwe, n’ibintu vyose bisubizwa kuri we"
  57,6,"Niyo yinjiza Ijoro m’Umutaga n’ukwinjiza Umutaga mw’Ijoro, nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"
  57,7,"Ni mwemere Imana y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo, kandi mutange muvyo Imana yabahaye, rero abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri muri mwebwe n’ugutanga ivyo mufise, abantu nkabo bari n’impembo niniya cane"
  57,8,"Mbega mumeze gute mwebwe mutemera Imana y’ukuri, mugihe intumwa y’Imana iba hamagarira kwemera Umuremyi wanyu, nayo ikaba yaramaze kwakira amasezerano kuri mwebwe, nimwaba mwemera bimwe bivuye k’umitima yanyu"
  57,9,"Niyo imanura amajambo yayo y’ukuri kandi ari k’umugaragaro ku ntumwa yayo kugira ngo ibakure mu mwijima ngo ibajane ahari umuco, ntankeka Imana niyo ihumuye kandi niyo nyene imigisha ihagije"
  57,10,"Mbega mubayeho gute ko muda tanga munzira y’Imana, n’ibisigi vyo mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi ni vy’Imana, kandi ntibangana bamwe muri mwebwe mubatanze imbere y’intsinzi n’ukubandanya kurwana, abo bantu nibo bafise iteka rininiya gusumba bamwe batanze ivyabo munyuma n’ukurwana, n’Imana yara bemereye ineza abo bantu bose kuko Imana niyo ifise inkuru z’ivyo bagira vyose"
  57,11,Ni nde muri mwebwe azoha Imana umwenda mwiza kugira ngo imwongereze incuro nyinshi hanyuma aze aronke impembo nziza
  57,12,"Umusi uzobona aba Isilamu b’abagabo hamwe naba Isilamu kazi imico yabo igenda imbere yabo n’iburyo bwabo, umunezero nu wuno musi muronkejwe imirima icamwo inzuzi imbere yanyu n’ukuba mwo mu buzima bwanyu bwose, iyo niyo ntsinzi niniya kuribo"
  57,13,"Umusi ababeshi b’abagabo hamwe n’ababeshi b’abagore bazo vuga babwira abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- nimu turindire kugira ngo turonke ahabona mumico yanyu, nabo bace babwirwa bati:- ni musubire inyuma yanyu muje kurondera umuco wanyu, hanyuma hashirwe hagati yabo uruzitiro rufise urugi, murirwo harimwo imigisha, no hanze k’uruhande yarwo rw’imbere yaho hari ibihano bikaze cane"
  57,14,"Bazoba hamagara ba babwire bati:- mbega ntitwari kumwe namwe? Nabo bazobishura bati:- egome, mugabo mwebwe nimwe mwijanye mubu hakanyi nu kurindira yuko amabi ashikira aba Isilamu, namwe muca mwitera amakenga n’ivyipfuzo vy’imitima yanyu yipfuza vyabahenze, kugeza naho itegeko ry’Imana ryaba shikira, n’umubeshi arabahenda kunkuru z’Imana"
  57,15,"Rero uno musi iwanyu ntakizo bakombora canke kuri barya bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, kuko ubwicaro bwanyu n’ubwo mu muriro udahera bukaba aribwo bubakwiye, naho n’ingaruka mbi cane"
  57,16,"Mbega umwanya nturashika gusa kubemeye yuko imitima yabo yogamburuka mu kwibuka Imana hamwe no kubintu vy’ukuri vyamanuwe, kandi ntibabe nkabamwe bahawe igitabu aho hambere n’umwanya wabo ubabera muremure, rero imitima yabo yaciye iba nk’urutare hanyuma benshi muribo baciye biyonkora"
  57,17,"Nimumenye yuko Imana inagisha Isi mugihe yari yarapfuye, ntankeka tubamenyesheje ibimenyetso vy’ubushobozi bwacu kugira ngo mutahure neza"
  57,18,"Mu vy’ukuri abagabo batanga imperezwa zabo, hamwe n’abapfasoni batanga imperezwa zabo, na bamwe baha umwenda mwiza Imana, abo bantu bazo kwongerezwa incuro zibiri bateko bahabwe impembo nziza"
  57,19,"Na bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa zayo, abo nibo bemezi n’ivyabona imbere y’Umuremyi wabo, bazoronswa impembo zabo hamwe n’imico yabo, mugabo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’uguhakana amajambo yacu, abo nibo bantu bo mu muriro udahera"
  57,20,"Mumenye yuko ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi bumeze nk’urukino n’ikintu c’ubusa n’isharizo ry’ukwinezereza hagati yanyu gusa, hamwe n’ukwiyerekana kw’amatungo n’ibibondo vyanyu, rero ni nk’imvura inezereza abarimyi kubera umwimbu wabo, mu nyuma ya vyose ugaca ubona vyose vyumye n’amabara yavyo aciye aba ay’umuhondo hanyuma ugaca uba nk’imizira ata kintu kirimwo, no k’umusi w’imperuka hariho ibihano bikaze cane, n’ikigongwe c’Imana hamwe n’Impuhwe zayo, rero nta buzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi atari ukwinezereza gusa guhenda"
  57,21,"Ni mwihute cane mu kuronswa imbabazi z’Umuremi wanyu hamwe n’Ijuru, ubwaguke bwayo ni nk’ubwaguke bw’Ijuru n’Isi, bwabikiwe bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’intumwa zayo, iyo niyo ngabirano y’Imana iha uwo yishakiye, nayo niyo nyene ingabirano niniya"
  57,22,"Nti haba ivyago ngaha kw’Isi canke mu mitima yanyu, atari uko biba vyamaze kwandikwa mugitabu c’Imana imbere yuko tubirema, mu vy’ukuri ivyo n’ibintu vyoroshe ku Mana"
  57,23,"Kugira ngo ntimu debukirwe cane kukintu cabatakaranye, kandi ntimunezerwe cane kuvyo Imana yabahaye, n’Imana nti kunda umuntu yishima n’ukwihayagiza"
  57,24,"N’abigira ingumyi n’ugutegeka abantu ngo babe ingumyi nkabo, n’uwuhindukira kuri ivyo Imana ntizo mwitaho kuko niyo ifise amatungo n’ugushimirwa"
  57,25,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraba shikirije intumwa zacu zifise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, dutako tumanura ibitabu n’ubutungane tukaba twaramanuye icuma gifise inguvu nyinshi cane n’akamaro kubantu, rero kugira ngo Imana imenyeshe uwo ikingira hamwe n’intumwa zayo mugihe batayibona iyo Mana , mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubushobozi n’intsinzi nyakuri"
  57,26,"Ntankeka twebwe twara mutwaye intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) hanyuma dushiraho mu ruvyaro rwabo ubutumwa bw’Imana hamwe n’igitabu, mugabo muribo bari barongotse n’abandi muribo bariyonkoye"
  57,27,"Hanyuma tubakurikiza intumwa zacu hanyuma dukurikiza intumwa y’Imana Issa mwene Mariyamu (iii) tumuha igitabu c’Imana c’Injili, hanyuma dushira mumitima yabamwe bamu kurikira ihumure, n’ukutubaka izabo n’ivyo batanguje kubwabo bonyene, twebwe ntitwa bandikiye ivyo bagira kugira ngo barondere impuhwe z’Imana, mugabo ntiba kurikiye nkuko vyategekanijwe gukurikizwa, hanyuma duha bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri muribo impembo yabo, na benshi muribo n’abiyonkoye"
  57,28,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana y’ukuri, nimu gamburukire Imana yanyu, hamwe n’intumwa yayo, kuko niyo izobaha ibice bibiri mumpuhwe zayo, kandi izoba girira umuco muzojana nawo mw’ijuru, kandi izobagirira ikigongwe, n’Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe nyinshi zihagije"
  57,29,"Kugira ngo abantu bahawe ibitabu vy’Imana bamenye yuko ata bubasha ubwaribwo bwose bafise kumigisha y’Imana, n’imigisha yose iri muminwe y’Imana, iha iyo migisha uwo yishakiye, nayo niyo nyene iyo migisha mikuru"
  58,1,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana iramaze kwumva imvugo y’umupfasoni aharira na wewe kubera umunega wiwe, kandi akabirega imbere y’Imana, nayo ikaba yumva ibihari vyanyu, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo yumva kandi niyo ibona"
  58,2,"Bamwe muri mwebwe bahamagara aba tambukanyi babo yuko ari banyina babo abo si banyina babo, kuko ntibari kuba banyina babo atari bamwe babavyaye, rero bavuga imvugo mbi niy’ububeshi, n’Imana niyo nyene imbabazi n’ikigongwe gihagije"
  58,3,"Na bamwe bahamagara abakenyezi babo yuko ari banyina babo, hanyuma bagasubira kuvuga muri yamvugo bavuga, rero nibahe umushumvyi uburenganzira bwiwe bw’ukwidegemvya imbere yuko bahuza nabo ibitsina, murahawe igabisho kuri ibi vyose, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo mugira vyose"
  58,4,"N’uwutazo ronka uwo mushumvyi ni yisonzeshe amezi abiri akurikirana imbere yuko bahuza ibitsina nuwo mukenyezi wiwe, nuwudashoboye kugira ivyo vyose, narishe abakene mirongo itandatu (60) aha mubwiwe gutyo kugira ngo mwemere Imana yanyu y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo, rero izo n’imbibe z’Imana, no kubatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri hariho ibihano bibabaza cane"
  58,5,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahiganwa n’Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo, abo bantu bazo teterezwa nkuko bateterejwe abamyeho imbere yabo, kandi turamaze kumanura amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ari k’umugaragaro, n’abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bazoronka ibihano bizoba tetereza"
  58,6,"Umusi Imana izozura abantu bose hanyuma ibabwire ivyo bagize vyose, nayo yabifashe nka nkama, nabo baravyibagiye, n’Imana niyo cabona kubintu vyose"
  58,7,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mumajuru yose hamwe n’ibiri kw’Isi? Ntihaboneka ubwongorerano bw’abantu batatu atari uko nayo iba ari iya kane muribo, canke abantu batanu atari uko ari iya gatandatu muribo, na bakeya cane gusumba abo, canke benshi gusumba abo, nuko iba iri kumwe nabo bose aho bari hose, hanyuma k’umusi w’imperuka izobabwira ivyo bagize vyose, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  58,8,"Ntubona bamwe babuzwa kwongorerana hanyuma barasubira kuvyo babujijwe, bakongorerana kubintu vy’ibicumuro hamwe nivy’ubwishime hamwe n’ivyukwiyonkora ku ntumwa y’Imana, n’igihe bashitse iwawe bakuramutsa n’indamutso itari indamutso yategetswe n’Imana mu kuramutswa kuriyo, bagaca bavuga mu mitima yabo bati:- mbega ni kuki Imana itaduhana kuri ibi vyose tuvuga, rero umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu uzoba uhagije kuribo mu kubahana bazowinjira mwo, naho n’ahantu habi cane kubo subizwayo"
  58,9,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, mugihe mwongoreranye n’abandi ntimwongorerane kubintu bijanye n’ibicumuro hamwe n’ukwishima n’uguhakana intumwa yayo, ahubwo ni muganire hejuru y’ukugira ineza n’ukutagira amabi, kandi nuku gamburukira Imana kuko kuriyo niho muzo kwegeranywa mwese"
  58,10,"Mu vy’ukuri ibiganiro bibi bivanye na Shetani kugira ngo ibatetereze bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri, mugabo ntishobora kuba girira inabi ku kintu icarico cose atari Imana yonyene ibishatse, rero aba Isilamu ni bizere Imana yabo gusa"
  58,11,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, mugihe mubwiwe gutanga umwanya w’ukwicaramwo ku bagenzi banyu, ni muwutange uwo mwanya, n’Imana izobagirira ikibanza ngaha kw’Isi no mw’Ijuru, kandi havuzwe hati:- ni muhaguruke nimuce mugenda, Imana izoba rerura bamwe bemeye bimwe vy’ukuri muri mwebwe, hamwe n’abahawe ubumenyi nibo bazohabwa iteka gusumba, n’Imana niyo ifise inkuru zivyo mugira vyose"
  58,12,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, mugihe muvugishije intumwa y’Imana ni mutange imperezwa imbere y’ukumuvugisha, ivyo nivyo vyiza kuri mwebwe nukuba sukura cane, rero ni mutaronka ico mutanga, rero ni kuMana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  58,13,"Oh! murabona ingorane z’ugutanguza izo mperezwa imbere y’ukuyivugisha? Ni mwagira gutyo n’Imana izoba girira ikigongwe, rero nimuhagarike amasengesho kandi mutange n’imperezwa nuku gamburukira Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo, n’Imana irafise inkuru z’ivyo mugira vyose"
  58,14,"Ntubabona bamwe bagize ubucuti hamwe n’abantu bashavuriwe n’Imana, abo ntibari kumwe namwe, kandi ntibari kumwe nabo, kandi barahira k’ububeshi mugihe bazi y’uko ari ababeshi"
  58,15,"Imana yaraba teguriye ibihano bikaze cane, mu vy’ukuri muvyo bahora bagira n’ibintu bibi cane"
  58,16,"Bagize indahiro zabo kuba arizo nkinzo zabo n’ukuzitira inzira yagenywe n’Imana, rero kuribo hazoba ibihano biba mara maza"
  58,17,"Amatungo yabo hamwe n’ibibondo vyabo ntaco bizoba marira n’ikintu na kimwe imbere y’Imana, abo nibo bantu bo mu muriro udahera, muriwo bazo wuba mwo mubuzima bwabo bwose"
  58,18,"Umusi Imana izozura abantu bose hanyuma barahire nkuko barahira iwanyu, bazo kwikeka yuko baronse ikintu c’ububeshi, mu vy’ukuri abo nibo babeshi nyakuri"
  58,19,"Shetani yarabicariye mukubibagiza kwibuka Imana yabo y’ukuri, uwo niwo murwi wa Shetani, kandi ni mutegere neza mu vy’ukuri umurwi wa Shetani niwo ufise uruhombo"
  58,20,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo abo ni muri bamwe bazoteterwa
  58,21,"Imana iramaze kwandika, yuko atankeka jewe nzotsinda hamwe n’intumwa zanje zose, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi n’intsinzi ihagije"
  58,22,"Nturonka abantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka yuko baba kunda bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo, naho boba ari abavyeyi babo, canke ibibondo vyabo, canke bene wabo, canke incuti zabo, abo nibo banditswe mu mitima yabo n’ukwemera kwabo n’ukubashiramwo ubushobozi k’umutima uvuye iwe, kandi izobinjiza mu mirima icamwo inzuzi imbere yabo, iyo niyo bazobayo mu buzima bwabo bwose, n’Imana yarabemereye kuribo, nabo barayemereye"
  59,1,"Ibiri mu majuru no kw’Isi nivyo bihayagiza Imana, nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  59,2,"Nayo niyo yakuye aba hakanye mu bantu bahawe igitabu c’Imana gitagatifu mu mazu yabo, mugihe c’ukwimuka kwabo kwa mbere, ntimwiketse yuko abo bantu bazovayo, nabo biketse yuko inzitiro zabo zizoba kingira ku Mana, mugabo Imana yabashikiye ahantu batizeye, n’ugushiraho ubwoba mu mitima yabo, baca baguma basenyura inzu zabo n’amaboko yabo, hamwe n’amaboko yaba Isilamu, rero mwebwe mufise amaso, nimutegere neza"
  59,3,"Iyo Imana itabandikira ubuhungiro bw’abo, yari kubahanira ngaha kw’Isi, no k’umusi w’imperuka bazoronka ibihano vy’umuriro udahera"
  59,4,"Ibi vyose nuko bahakanye Imana y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo, rero uwahakanye Imana amenye yuko Imana ikaze cane muguhana"
  59,5,"Igiti c’umutende icarico cose mwaciye canke mwasigaje kigihagaze kumatsina yaco, vyose ivyo ni kw’itegeko ry’Imana ry’ukuba tetereza abahonyanga amategeko y’Imana"
  59,6,"N’amatungo Imana yashikirije intumwa yayo iyakuye iwabo ntimwa yakoresheje gihuti huti kuri za farasi canke kuri za ngamiya, mugabo Imana iha ubutegetsi bwayo kuntumwa zayo, hejuru yabo yishakiye nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  59,7,"Amatungo Imana yashikirije kuntumwa yiwe iyakuye ku bantu bisagara, n’ukubera Imana hamwe n’intumwa yiwe hamwe n’abagenzi biwe, hamwe n’impfuvyi, n’aboro, hamwe n’uwuri mu rugendo rwiwe rwononekaye kugira ngo ntihabe ihiganwa hagati y’abatunzi banyu gusa, rero muvyo intumwa y’Imana yabahaye ni muvyakire, nico ibatujije kugira ntimu cegere, kandi mutinye Imana yanyu mu vy’ukuri Imana irakaze cane muguhana"
  59,8,"Ni bahabwe abo bakene bahunze kandi birukanywe mu mazu yabo hamwe n’amatungo yabo, kubera imigisha y’Imana hamwe n’impuhwe zayo hamwe n’ugukingira idini ry’Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo, abo rero nibo baIsilamu b’ukuri"
  59,9,"Na bamwe bagira icumbiko ryabo ngaha IMadina n’ugusukura ubu Isilamu imbere yabo, n’ukuba kunda abo bantu bimukiye iwabo, kandi ataco baronka, kandi badafise akariganga muhogo mu bikiriza vyabo kuri ivyo bahawe, kandi bakaba babakunda gusumba imitima yabo naho kuribo bafise uburyo bubayabaye, kandi bateshejwe nukuba ingumyi y’imitima yabo, abo nibo bafise intsinzi y’ukuri"
  59,10,"N’abaje mu nyuma zabo bavuga bati:- ewe Muremyi wacu, n’utugirire ikigongwe hamwe na bene wacu bashengeye imbere yacu, mw’idini rya Isilamu, kandi ntushire mu mitima yacu inzikira y’ukurira bene wacu baba Isilamu, Muremyi wacu mu vy’ukuri wewe uri intungane cane, n’impuhwe zihagije"
  59,11,"Ntubona b’ababeshi babwira bene wabo b’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bo mu bantu bahawe igitabu aribo Bayahudi bavuze bati:- ni mwakurwa ngaha tuzojana namwe, kandi ntituzo gamburukira uwariwe wese hejuru yanyu, ni mwaterwa tuzoba fasha, n’Imana niyo cabona yuko abo bantu ari ababeshi"
  59,12,"Nibirukanwa ntibazo sohoka nabo, niba terwa ntibazo bafasha, niba bafasha mu vy’ukuri bazohindura imigongo yabo, hanyuma nti bazoronka uwubakingira"
  59,13,"Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe aba Isilamu muratinywa cane mu mitima yabo gusumba uko batinya Imana y’ukuri, kuko n’abantu badategera icarico cose"
  59,14,"Ntibazo rwana namwe bari mumirwi, atari mu bisagara vyabo bikingiwe canke inyuma y’impome, rero indwano yabo iri hagati yabo ni niniya, umengo yuko bari urunani, mugihe imitima yabo itandukanye, ivyo vyose n’ukubera yuko ari abantu badafise ubwenge"
  59,15,"Uko bameze ninka bamwe bari imbere yabo ubu vuba, barahonjeje amabi y’ivyo bagize, kandi bazoronka ibihano bibabaza cane"
  59,16,"Ni nkaho Shetani mugihe ibwiye umuntu ngo n’ucumure, yaheza gucumura igaca imubwira iti:- jewe sindi kumwe nawe, mu vy’ukuri jewe ndatinya Imana, Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  59,17,"Rero amaherezo yabo bantu uko ari babiri, kwari ukwinjizwa mu muriro udahera n’ukubayo mu buzima bwabo bwose, iyo rero niyo mpembo y’abahemukiye imitima yabo"
  59,18,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimu gamburukire Imana yanyu, n’umuntu uwariwe wese arabe ivyo atanguza mu kugira kubera akazoza kiwe k’ejo, kandi mu gamburukire Imana yanyu y’ukuri mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise inkuru y’ivyo mugira vyose"
  59,19,"Kandi ntimube nkabarya bibagiye Imana yabo y’ukuri, nayo ira bibagiza kumitima yabo, abantu nkabo nibo biyonkozi bakuru"
  59,20,"Ntibangana abantu bo mumuriro udahera hamwe n’abantu bo mw’ijuru, abantu bo mw’juru nibo bene intsinzi"
  59,21,"Iyo tumanura iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu hejuru y’umusozi, wari kuwubona ugamburuka n’ukumanyuka kubera ugutinya Imana, ubu nabwo n’uburorero twereka abantu kugira ngo biyumvire"
  59,22,"Niyo Mana atayindi Mana isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyinyegeje n’ibiboneka, kandi ikaba ariyo nyene imigisha mininiya na nyene imigisha mito mito"
  59,23,"Niyo Mana atayindi Mana isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, n’umwami mutagatifu, nyene amahoro, n’umutanzi w’amahoro, agendesha ibintu vyiwe, n’ukw’iganza, ikagira ivyo ishatse, niyo nkuru iri kure n’abo bayigereranya ko n’ibindi bintu"
  59,24,"Niwe Mana muremyi n’umuhinguzi, n’umugizi w’amashusho atandukanye y’ibiremwa vyose, nyene amazina meza, aninahazwa mu Majuru no kw’Isi, kandi niyo ifise inguvu n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  60,1,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimugire abansi banje hamwe n’abansi banyu kuba aribo bagenzi banyu mushikiriza inkuru zanyu kubera ubugenzi bwanyu gusa, mugihe bahakana ukuri kwama kwabashikiye n’ukwirukana intumwa y’Imana hamwe namwe, kubera yuko mwemera Imana ariyo muremyi wanyu, n’igihe mwitanze mugiye k’urugamba ariyo nzira yanje, n’ukurondera ikigongwe canje, muca mutanga amabanga yanyu y’ingwano kubera urukundo rwanyu mubafitiye, ntimusubire kugira ivyo, nanje ndafise ubumenyi bw’ivyo munyegeza hamwe n’ivyo muserura, rero n’uwugira ivyo vyose muri mwebwe amenye yuko yataye inzira y’ukuri"
  60,2,"Bahuye namwe baca baba abansi banyu, n’ukuba gororera ibiganza vyabo, n’indimi zabo z’ububisha bwabo, bakipfuza yuko mwohemuka"
  60,3,"Ntaco bazoba marira abo bagenzi banyu, canke ibibondo vyanyu k’umusi w’imperuka, n’Imana izo tandukanya hagati yanyu, nayo niyo ibona ibintu vyose mugira"
  60,4,"Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe murafise akarorero keza kuntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) hamwe nabo yari kumwe nabo, mugihe babwira bagenzi babo bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi kure namwe, hamwe n’ivyo musenga bidatumberanye ni vy’Imana, rero turabanse kuko bimaze kugaragara ubwansi n’urwankano rw’urutavana ko ruri hagati yacu namwe kugeza aho muzo kwemera Imana yonyene rudende, dukuye mwo imvugo y’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yabwiye umuvyeyi wiwe ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzogusabira ikigongwe mugabo nta bubasha mfise bw’ikintu na kimwe kubera wewe imbere y’Imana, rero ntimwigane iri jambo ryiwe ry’ukuba sabira igisabisho abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri, ahubwo nimuvuge muti:- Muremyi wacu, twizeye kuri wewe, kandi duhindukiye gutumbera iwawe, n’iwawe gusa niho hari igaruka rya twese"
  60,5,"Muremyi wacu, ntutugirire amananiza kuri babantu bahakanye Imana y’ukuri, kandi utugirire ikigongwe, mu vy’ukuri ni wewe ufise ubushobozi bukwiye n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  60,6,"Mu vy’ukuri karabaye akarorero keza kuri mwebwe kunyifato yabo, k’uwutinya Imana yiwe y’ukuri hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka, rero n’uwutitaho kuri ibi vyose, Imana niyo ifise ubushobozi buhayagizwa hose"
  60,7,"Nkumbure Imana izoshiramwo urukundo hagati yanyu hamwe nabo bansi banyu, nayo niyo ifise ubushobozi buhagije kandi niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  60,8,"Imana ntibabuza kugirira ineza n’ubutungane bamwe batarwanye namwe kubera idini, kandi bata birukanye mu bisagara vyanyu, mu vy’ukuri Imana irakunda abagira ubutungane"
  60,9,"Imana ibabuza kuri barya barwana namwe mu nzira y’idini ry’Imana n’ukubirukana mubisagara vyanyu, kandi bagafasha mu kwirukanwa kwanyu n’ukubagira abagenzi banyu, rero abagira kuba aribo bagenzi babo abo nibo bahemu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  60,10,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ni mwashikirwa n’abakenyezi baba Isilamu kazi bimuka, ni mubahe ibibazo, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi kubasumba mu kwemera kw’abo, nimwabona yuko ari aba Isilamu kazi b’ukuri ntimubasubize inyuma kuri barya batemera Imana y’abo y’ukuri, rero abo bakenyezi ntibagifise uburenga nzira kuri abo bagabo batemera imana yabo y’ukuri, nabo bagabo batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri ntibagifise uburenga nzira kuribo, rero ni mubasubize udushimwe twabo abo bagabo batanze, kandi kuri mwebwe ntakosa ririmwo mu kwubakana nabo nimwa baha udushimwe twabo, mugabo ntimubabike abo bakenyezi babatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri muri uwo murwi w’ukwubaka izabo muri mwebwe, kandi mubasabe kubashaka kwubakana nabo babahe udushimwe twabo nkutwo batanze, rero ubu nibwo butungane bw’Imana yategetse, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  60,11,"Niya hunga umwe mubakenyezi banyu, akagenda kubana n’umwe mubahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, hagaca haboneka akarusho kuri mwebwe nimubahe babakenyezi bahunga kubingana n’agashimwe batanze, kandi mutinye Imana yanyu mwemera"
  60,12,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, niwashikirwa n’abakenyezi bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bakwemerera yuko batazo gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, canke batazo kwiba, canke batazo shurashura, canke batazo kwica ibibondo vyabo, canke batazo kwadukana n’ivyo biyadukanije , biturutse kumaboko yabo n’amaguru yabo, kandi bakaba batazo kwiyonkora kuri wewe kw’ijambo ryiza, rero nimuhane amasezerano nabo, kandi ubasabire ikigongwe ku Mana, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  60,13,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimugiriranire ubucuti buhanitse n’abantu Imana yashavuriye, kandi baramaze kwihebura"
  61,1,"Ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi bihayagiza Imana, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  61,2,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ni kuki muvuga ivyo mudashira mungiro"
  61,3,N’ibishavuza imbere y’Imana kuvuga ivyo mudashira mungiro
  61,4,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana ikunda bamwe barwanira munzira yayo bari kumirongo, nkuko ari inyubakwa yateranijwe n’iyindi"
  61,5,"Ubibutse wewe ntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) igihe wabwira abantu bawe uti:- mwebwe bantu banje, ni kuki munshavuza mugihe mufise ubumenyi yuko jewe nd’intumwa y’Imana kuri mwebwe, rero mugihe babandanije bagira amabi yabo, Imana yaciye irekura imitima yabo izimire, n’Imana ntirongora abantu babi nkabo biyonkoye"
  61,6,"Mugihe intumwa y’Imana Issa mwene Mariyamu (iii) yavuga ati:- mwebwe bene Israeri, jewe nd’intumwa y’Imana kuri mwebwe nemeza ivyabaye imbere yanje biri mugitabu gitagatifu c’Imana ca Taurati n’ugushikiriza inkuru nziza y’intumwa y’Imana izoza inyuma yanje azoba afise izina ryiwe ryitwa Ahmadi, mugabo igihe yabashikira afise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro baciye bavuga bati:- uku n’uguhendwa kuri k’umugaragaro"
  61,7,"None ni nde muhemu mukuru w’umutima wiwe gusumba uwubeshera Imana kandi ahamagarirwa mw’idini rya isilamu, n’Imana ntirongora abahemukira imitima yabo"
  61,8,"Bagomba kuzimya umuco w’Imana bakoresheje iminwa yabo, n’Imana izoshikana umuco wayo naho abahakanyi b’Imana bazoshavura"
  61,9,Niyo yarungitse intumwa yiwe n’uburongozi hamwe n’idini ry’ukuri kugira ngo idini ry’Imana ritsinde amadini yose naho abagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu bazoshavura
  61,10,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, mbega ndaba menyesheje ibidandazwa bizoba rokora n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  61,11,"Ni mwemere Imana yanyu y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yiwe, kandi murwanire idini ry’Imana kumatungo yanyu n’imitima yanyu, ivyo nivyo vyiza kuri mwebwe, nimwaba mubizi"
  61,12,"Imana izoba hanagurira ibicumuro vyanyu n’ukubinjiza mu mirima icamwo inzuzi imbere yabo, hamwe n’ubwicaro bwiza buri muri iyo mirima y’ubuzima bwabo bwose, iyo niyo ntsinzi niniya"
  61,13,"N’ikindi mukunda nabwo n’uburokoke buvuye ku Mana n’intsinzi iri hafi cane, rero n’ubamenyeshe inkuru nziza aba Isilamu bose"
  61,14,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimube abafasha b’Imana nkuko intumwa y’Imana Issa mwene Mariyamu (iii) yabwira incoreke ziwe ati:- nibande bafasha banje kubera Imana, za ncoreke ziwe zimwishura ziti:- ni twebwe bafasha b’Imana, rero umurwi wa bene Israeri riremera, n’uwundi murwi nawo urahakana, tubatera intege bamwe bemera hejuru y’abansi babo n’ukuba aribo bene intsinzi nyakuri"
  62,1,"Ibiri mu majuru no kw’Isi vyose bihayagiza Imana, Umwami, Mutagatifu nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  62,2,"Niyo yazanye intumwa y’Imana mu bantu batazi gusoma, avuye muribo, abasomera amajambo y’Imana matagatifu n’ukuba sukura n’ukubigisha igitabu c’Imana gitagatifu hamwe n’ubuhizi, n’imbere yibi vyose bari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  62,3,"N’abandi muribo batariyunga nabo, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  62,4,"Iyo n’imigisha y’Imana iha uwo yishakiye, nayo niyo nyene imigisha mininiya"
  62,5,"Akarorero, ni bamwe bahawe igitabu c’Imana gitagatifu ca Taurati hanyuma ntiba cakira mu kugikoresha, ni nk’indogobwe yikoreye ibitabu bininiya kuriyo ata gahengwe kuriyo, aka n’akarorero kabi cane k’abantu bahakanye amajambo y’Imana matagatifu nayo Imana ntirongora abantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  62,6,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe Bayahudi nimwaba mwihayagiza yuko mwebwe muri abakunzi b’Imana hatarimwo abandi bantu, rero ni mwipfuze urupfu nimwaba muvugisha ukuri kwama"
  62,7,"Mugabo ntibazo kwipfuza urwo rupfu, kubera ivyo batanguje kugira n’amaboko yabo n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’abahemukiye imitima yabo"
  62,8,"Vuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri uru rupfu muhunga, ntankeka muzohura narwo, hanyuma muze musubizwe k’uwufise ubumenyi bw’amabanga yose nayari k’umugaragaro aho niho izoba menyesha ivyo mwahora mugira vyose"
  62,9,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, niha hamagarwa kubijanye n’amasengesho y’umusi wa gatanu, ni mugende ningoga na ningoga kuyivuga Imana kandi mureke kudandaza, mugize gutyo nivyo vyiza kuri mwebwe ni mwaba mufise ubumenyi buhagije"
  62,10,"Ayo masengesho arangiye nimu kwiragire kw’isi yose murondere imigisha y’Imana, kandi mwibuke Imana kenshi na kenshi, kugira ngo muronke intsinzi nyakuri"
  62,11,"Mugihe babonye ibidandazwa canke ibikinisho baca bavyirukirako bakagusiga uhagaze, wewe n’uvuge uti:- ibiri kumana nivyo vyiza gusumba urwo rukino n’ibidandazwa, n’Imana niyo ntore mugutanga imigisha yayo"
  63,1,"Niwashikirwa n’ababeshi bavuga bati:- twebwe turi ivyabona yuko mu vy’ukuri wewe uri intumwa y’Imana, n’Imana irafise ubumenyi buhagije yuko wewe uri intumwa y’Imana, n’Imana niyo cabona yuko mu vy’ukuri ababeshi ari ababeshi gusa"
  63,2,"Bagize indahiro zabo kuba arizo nkinzo zabo zibakingira, baca bikingira mugucishwa munzira y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri muvyo bahora bagira ni bibi cane"
  63,3,"N’ivyo vyose nuko bemeye, munyuma yaho barahakana, kuri ivyo ikidodo caratewe kumitima yabo, kuri ivyo nta nakimwe bazi"
  63,4,"Ubabonye imibiri yabo irabereye neza, niyo bariko baravuga urumva mumvugo zabo mugabo kuribo ninka kumwe kw’ibiti vya hagaze aho biri womengo igikakaje kiri hejuru yabo, rero abo nibo bansi mwirinde kuribo, n’Imana n’ibicire kure, none ni kuki batirigana k’ukuri"
  63,5,"Mugihe babwiwe bati:- nimuze kugira ngo intumwa y’Imana ibasabire ikigongwe, baca bahindura imitwe yabo ukababona bikingiye n’ukwishima yuko aribo bantu bakuru"
  63,6,"Ni vyiza kuribo ubasabiye ikigongwe canke utakibasabiye ico kigongwe Imana ntizo kibagirira, mu vy’ukuri Imana ntirongora abantu biyonkoye kuriyo"
  63,7,"Nibo bavuga y’uko:- ntimutange amatungo yanyu kubera abari kumwe n’intumwa y’Imana kugira ngo baveho baje kure, nayo ububiko bw’Amajuru n’Isi n’ubw’Imana, mugabo ababeshi nta nakimwe bazi"
  63,8,"Bavuga bati:- nitwagaruka mu gisagara c’IMadinat, nyene ubutagatifu azo kwirukana nyarucari na nyene iteka nyakuri n’Imana hamwe n’intumwa yiwe hamwe naba Isilamu, mugabo abo babeshi nta nakimwe bazi"
  63,9,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntabibagize amatungo yanyu canke ibibondo vyanyu mu kutibuka Imana, n’abagira ivyo vyose nibo bari m’uruhombo"
  63,10,"Nimutange muvyo twabahaye imbere yuko umwe muri mwebwe atara shikirwa n’urupfu, hanyuma agaca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, nundindirize n’umwanya mutoyi ngatanga imperezwa hanyuma nkaba mubantu bagira ineza"
  63,11,"Mugabo Imana ntizo rindiriza umutima w’umuntu uwariwe wese washikiwe n’urupfu rwawo, n’Imana niyo ifise inkuru yivyo mugira vyose"
  64,1,"Ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi vyose bininahaza Imana, ubwami ni rwayo n’ihayagizwa ryiza ni rwayo, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  64,2,"Niyo yabaremye mwese, n’abandi muri mwebwe batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri n’abandi muri mwebwe naba Isilamu, n’Imana niyo ibona ivyo mugira vyose"
  64,3,"Niyo yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri, n’ukugira amashusho yanyu, hanyuma ayo mashusho ayagira neza, n’ingaruka ya vyose iriwe"
  64,4,"Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mu Majuru no kw’Isi, n’ukumenya ivyo munyegeza nivyo muserura, nayo niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"
  64,5,"Mbega ntimwashikiwe n’inkuru ya bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baho hambere, bahonjeje amabi y’ibikorwa vyabo, nabo nibo bafise ibihano bibabaza cane"
  64,6,"Ivyo vyose n’ukubera intumwa z’Imana zabo zaguma zibashikira zifise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, mugabo bavuga bati:- abantu nkatwe nibo boturongora? Kuri ivyo barahakanye n’uguhindukira kurundi ruhande, n’Imana ntaco ikeneye, ahubwo irihagije kubwayo, kandi niyo ihayagizwa gusumba ibindi vyose"
  64,7,"Abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuga yuko batazozurwa, wewe n’uvuge uti:- ni kuki kw’ukuri k’Umuremyi wanje, mwebwe muzozurwa vyanka bikunda, kandi ningombwa yuko muzo menyeshwa ivyo mwagize vyose, kandi ivyo bintu n’ivyoroshe ku Mana"
  64,8,"Rero ni muyemere Imana yanyu y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo n’umuco twamanuye, n’Imana niyo ifise inkuru zivyo mugira vyose"
  64,9,"Umusi Imana izobakoranya mwese, kubera uwo musi w’ukwegeranywa, uwo niwo musi w’uruhombo rw’abantu babi, n’uwemera Imana yiwe y’ukuri izomu hanagurira amabi yiwe yose nukumwinjiza mu mirima yo mw’Ijuru icamwo inzuzi imbere yiwe, hanyuma baze babeyo mu buzima bwabo bwose, iyo niyo ntsinzi niniya"
  64,10,"Nabamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’uguhakana amajambo y’acu matagatifu, abo nibo bantu bo mumuriro udahera, bazobayo mu buzima bwabo bwose, naho hari ingaruka mbi cane kuribo"
  64,11,"Nta vyago ivyarivyo vyose bishika atari kw’itegeko ry’Imana, n’uwemera Imana yiwe y’ukuri niwe arongora umutima wiwe, n’Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  64,12,"Ni mugamburukire Imana yanyu y’ukuri n’intumwa yayo, ni mutitaho ni kuntumwa yacu gubashikiriza ubutumwa gusa buri kumugaragaro"
  64,13,"Imana, ntayindi isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, naba Isilamu nibizere Imana yonyene gusa"
  64,14,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, mu vy’ukuri bamwe mu bakenyezi banyu hamwe n’ibibondo vyanyu nibo bansi banyu, rero ni mwirinde kuribo nimwaba girira ikigongwe n’ukutitaho kuvyabaye n’uguhanagura ibiri mu mitima yanyu, nuko Imana ifise ikigongwe cinshi hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije"
  64,15,Ntankeka amatungo yanyu hamwe n’ibibondo vyanyu n’ibigeragezo kuri mwebwe bantu no kuMana niho hari impembo niniya cane
  64,16,"Ni mugamburukire Imana yanyu y’ukuri uko mubishoboye kwose, kandi mwumvirize muteko mugamburuke, kandi mutange ivyanyu mu nzira nziza bizoba ari vyiza ku mitima yanyu, n’abazo kingirwa nukutaba ingumyi y’imitima y’abo, abo nibo bene intsinzi nyakuri"
  64,17,"Nimwa begurira Imana ikimanyu ciza, izo bongerezako, kandi izoba girira ikigongwe, n’Imana niyo itanga imihezagiro myinshi kandi niyo ntungane"
  64,18,"Niyo yene kumenya ibiri mumbari hamwe n’ibiri k’umugaragaro, niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  65,1,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, nimwahukana n’abakenyezi banyu nimwahukane nabo mubihe c’ivyicaro vyabo vy’imihango yabo, kandi mugire ibiharuro c’ivyicaro vyabo vy’ukwahukana, kandi mugamburukire Imana ariyo Mana yanyu, kandi ntimu basohore mu mazu yabo, kandi ntibasohoke bonyene, mugabo nibagira amabi ayariyo yose k’umugaragaro, aho niho mushobora kubasohora, izo rero nizo mbibe z’Imana, n’uwurenga kuri izo mbibe z’Imana azoba yihemukiye k’umutima wiwe, kuko ntawufise ubumenyi yuko nkumbure Imana yoserura ikindi kintu munyuma yivyo vyose"
  65,2,"Rero ikiringo cabo kigeze, nimubane nabo mumahoro, canke mwahukane nabo mumahoro meza ntangere, kandi habe ivyabona bibiri vy’imvuga kuri muri mwebwe, kandi muhagarike ivyabona kubera Imana, uko niko atumwa umwe mubemera Imana yiwe y’ukuri hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka, n’uwutinya Imana yiwe y’ukuri imugirira inzira y’uburokoke"
  65,3,"Kandi imuha imigisha k’uburyo atayizera, n’uwizera Imana yiwe y’ukuri niyo imwuzuriza, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo imwuzuriza kuvyo yipfuza vyose, mu vy’ukuri Imana iramaze kugena ibintu vyose kuburinganire bwavyo bukwiye"
  65,4,"Na bamwe mubakenyezi banyu bahagaritse imihango yabo, ni mwaba mufise amakenga imisi y’ivyicaro vy’imihango yabo, n’amezi atatu, n’abatara ronka imihango yabo, hamwe n’abakenyezi bafise imbanyi ikiringo c’ukwicara kwabo n’igihe caho bazo kwibarukira, n’uwutinya Imana yiwe y’ukuri yama imugirira ibintu vyiwe kuba ari ivyoroshe"
  65,5,"Iryo n’itegeko ry’Imana yamanuye kuri mwebwe bantu, n’uwutinya Imana yiwe bimwe vy’ukuri imuhanagurira amabi yiwe yose n’ukumuha impembo niniya cane"
  65,6,"Ni mubagumize ngaho nyene mungo zanyu muba mwo, nkuko mubayeho, kandi nti mubagirire inabi n’ukubata mukaga, niba bafise imbanyi ni mubihanganire kugeza aho bazo kwibarukira, niba bonkereza ibibondo vyanyu mubahe agashiruka bute kabo, kandi mwumvikane kuneza, ni mwabona yuko hari agahaze hagati yanyu, n’iyonse ico kibondo uwundi muvyeyi"
  65,7,"Uwufise uburyo niyitange nkuko abishoboye, n’uwutishoboye k’uburyo bw’imigisha yiwe n’atange kuvyo Imana yamuhaye, kandi nayo ntihatagiza uwariwe wese atari kubingana nivyo yamuhaye, Imana izo muha, munyuma y’ingorane haze haboneke agahengwe"
  65,8,"N’ibisagara bingahe vyahonyanze amategeko y’Umuremyi wavyo hamwe n’intumwa zayo, natwe twayiharuriye ibiharuro bikomeye n’ukubihana kubihano bikaze cane"
  65,9,"Rero irahonja kumabi w’ivyo wagize, n’impera y’ibintu vyabo vyose rwari uruhombo gusa"
  65,10,"Imana yarabateguriye ibihano bikaze cane, rero nimu yigamburukire mwebwe mufise ubwenge, mwemeye bimwe vy’ukuri, mu vy’ukuri Imana rugira vyose yaraba manuriye icibutso"
  65,11,"Intumwa y’Imana ibasomera amajambo y’Imana matagatifu agaragaza ibikenewe vyose kugira ngo ibakure bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza, n’ukubakura mumwijima n’ukubinjiza mumuco, n’uwemera Imana yiwe y’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza izo mwinjiza mumajuru aca imbere yiwe inzuzi, baze babeyo mu buzima bwabo bwose n’Imana iramaze kumuha imigisha myiza"
  65,12,"Imana nirya yaremye Amajuru yose uko ari indwi, hamwe n’Isi kuba nk’akarorero k’ivyo nyene, rero amategeko aguma amanuka hagati yabo kugira ngo mumenye yuko Imana ariyo nyene ubushobozi bw’ibintu vyose, kandi ikikuje ibintu vyose, n’ukubimenya"
  66,1,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, ni kuki ubuza ivyarekuriwe kugirwa n’Imana, ukarondera ikigongwe kubakenyezi bawe n’Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe n’impuhwe gihagije"
  66,2,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana yarabahaye ubutungane bw’ukwugurura indahiro zanyu, n’Imana niyo Muremyi wanyu, kandi niyo nyene ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  66,3,"Kandi ubibutse igihe intumwa y’Imana yabwira umwe mubakenyezi biwe ijambo ry’ibanga, rero igihe yarisasagaje Imana nayo ica irari muserurira intumwa y’Imana munca make bimwe muvyo yavuze n’ugusigaza ayandi mabanga, rero mugihe yamubwira izo nkuru wamukenyezi wiwe yavuze ati:- ni nde yaguhaye izi nkuru? Nawe amwishura ati:- uwampaye izi nkuru nurya afise ubumenyi bw’ukuri n’inkuru z’ibintu vyose"
  66,4,"Nimwasaba ikigongwe ku Mana yanyu y’ukuri, nuko imitima yanyu yahengamye gatoyi, mugabo nimwa fashanya kubera intumwa y’Imana nuko Imana ari umukunzi wayo hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Jib’riylu, naba Isilamu b’intore bose, no hejuru yivyo vyose n’Abamarayika bazo fasha"
  66,5,"Nkumbure nimwahukana Umuremyi wiwe azomuha uwundi mutambukanyi atari muri mwebwe mubakenyezi b’intungane gusumba mwebwe, bakurikiza inkingi zubw’Isilamu n’ukwemera inkingi z’ukwemera kw’idini rya Isilamu, bagamburuka kandi basaba ikigongwe mugihe bakosheje, kandi bagira amasengesho n’ukugira ibikorwa vyinshi vyiza, kubamaze kwubaka izabo canke abatarubaka izabo"
  66,6,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ni mwirokore kumitima yanyu hamwe n’abantu banyu, hamwe n’umucanwa, inkwi zawo n’abantu hamwe n’amabuye, uwo mucanwa uhagarikiwe n’Abamarayika bakaze cane b’inguvu batadohokera Imana kumategeko yayo, kandi bakagira ivyo bategetswe kugira vyose"
  66,7,"Mwebwe mwahakanye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimwitwaze ivyarivyo vyose kuri uno musi, ntankeka muronswa impembo yivyo mwahora mugira"
  66,8,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimusabe ikigongwe ku Mana yanyu ikigongwe c’ukuri, nkumbure Umuremyi wanyu azoba hanagurira amabi yanyu n’ukubinjiza mu Majuru acamwo inzuzi imbere yayo, umusi waho Imana itazo tetereza intumwa yiwe canke abayemeye bari kumwe nayo, umuco wabo uzohora ugenda imbere yabo no kumpande zabo zose z’iburyo, bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu dukwirize uwo muco wacu kandi utugirire ikigongwe, mu vy’ukuri ni wewe nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  66,9,"Ewe ntumwa y’Imana, n’uhiganwe nabo bahakanyi batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’ababeshi, kandi ube ufise umukazo kuribo, n’ubwicaro bwabo nubwo mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, nayo n’ingaruka mbi cane"
  66,10,"Imana yaratanze akarorero kuri babantu babi bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, nawe n’umutambukanyi w’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) hamwe n’umutambukanyi w’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii), kuko bari mu bantu bacu beranda, mugabo baratiriganye ku mabanga yabo ntiba shobora kubafasha kukintu icarico cose imbere y’Imana, haca havugwa hati:- nimwinjire mu muriro udahera hamwe naba winjira mwo"
  66,11,"N’Imana yaratanze akarorero kuri bamwe bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri, k’umukenyezi wa Fir’auni igihe yavuga ati:- ewe Muremyi wanje, nunyubakire inzu mw’ijuru iri hafi yawe, hanyuma undokore nuyu Fir’auni hamwe n’ibikorwa vyiwe bibi bigaritse, kandi undokore n’abantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  66,12,"Na Mariyamu mwene Imrani (iii) yifashe runtu no k’umutima wiwe, duca duhuhera muriwe umutima wacu n’ukwemeza amajambo y’Umuremyi wiwe hamwe n’ibitabu vyayo, akaba yari mu bantu bagamburuka"
  67,1,"Araninahajwe uwufise muminwe yiwe ubwami bwose, kandi niwe nyene ubushobozi buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  67,2,"Niwe yaremye urupfu hamwe n’ubuzima kugira ngo ibagerageze imenye uwariwe muri mwebwe afise ibikorwa vyiza gusumba, nayo niyo nyene ubushobozi n’ikigongwe"
  67,3,"Niwe yaremye Amajuru yose uko ari indwi agerekeranye kuyandi, mbega ntubona itandukaniro iryariryo ryose mukurema kwa nyene imigisha, rero n’uhindukize amaso yawe ugume uvuga uti:- mbega urabona mwo ikosa"
  67,4,"Kandi garura amaso yawe kenshi na kenshi, hanyuma iryo jisho ryawe rizo garuka riteterewe nawe warushe"
  67,5,"Mu vy’ukuri twarasharije iri Juru riri hafi n’amatara, kandi twagize gutyo kugira ngo dukubite amashetani, kandi twabashiriye ho ibihano biteguye vy’umuriro waka n’inguvu nyinshi cane"
  67,6,"N’abahakanye Umuremyi wabo w’ukuri, hariho ibihano vy’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu n’ingaruka mbi imeze gute"
  67,7,Ni batabwa muriwo bazo kwumva isumo ryawo n’ingene umoka
  67,8,"Uregereje gusaduka kubera ishavu ryawo no hejuru y’abantu babi, uko hatawe mwo umurwi w’abantu babi, aba wucungereye nabo bazoba baza bati :- mbega ntimwashikiwe n’uwutuza"
  67,9,"Nabo bazo kwishura bati:- mbega ni kuki twashikiwe n’uwutuza? Mugabo twebwe twarahakanye n’ukuvuga duti:- Imana nta nakimwe yamanuye, namwe ntaho muri atari mubuzimire buniniya cane"
  67,10,"Bazovuga bati :- iyo tuba twumva canke iyo tuba dufise ubwenge ntitwari kuba abantu bo mumuriro udahera"
  67,11,"Baremeza ibicumuro vyabo, rero uguhonywa kwabo kuraba kwiye abo bantu bo mu muriro udahera"
  67,12,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batinya Umuremyi wabo nabo batamubona bazoronka imbabazi n’impembo niniya cane
  67,13,"Nimugire amabanga y’imvugo zanyu canke muziserure, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"
  67,14,Ntamenye uwaremye nayo ariyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibitazwi hamwe n’ibizwi
  67,15,"Niyo yagize Isi ngo ishobore gukora kubera mwebwe, rero ni mugenzure kumpande zayo zose, kandi mufungure kumigisha yayo, no kuriyo niho twese tuzo subirayo"
  67,16,"Mbega mwiyumvira yuko muri mumahoro ku Mana iyo mw’ijuru itazoba cinyiriza kw’Isi, mukaza mubona Isi iranyiganze"
  67,17,"Canke mwiyumvira yuko muri mumahoro ku Mana iri mw’ijuru ubwami bwiwe ni buniniya yuko itazoba zanira igihuhusi kivanzwe mwo umusenyi n’amabuye, niho muzomenya ituza ryanje"
  67,18,"Ntankeka barahakanye abariho imbere yabo, mbega kwabaye gute ugushavura kwanje"
  67,19,"Mbega ntibabona inyoni ziri hejuru yabo ingene zigorora amababa yazo n’ukuyazinga, nta n’umwe azi zitirira atari Imana nyene imigisha myinshi, mu vy’ukuri niyo ibona ibintu vyose"
  67,20,Canke n’izihe ngabo zanyu zishobora kuba kingira atari nyene imigisha myinshi? Ntaba hakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri atari uguhendwa gusa
  67,21,Canke ni nde azobaha imigisha mugihe ibazitiriye iyo migisha yayo ahubwo babandanya mu bwiyonkore bwabo n’urwankano gusa
  67,22,"Mbega uwugenda ajunjamitse umutwe wiwe atamerewe neza, mbega niwe mweranda, canke uwugenda atumbereye inzira igororotse"
  67,23,"Vuga uti:- niyo yabaremye n’ukubaha amatwi n’amaso hamwe n’imitima, rero nibakeyi cane bashima iyo ngabirano yanyu"
  67,24,"Vuga uti:- niyo yabatandukanije kw’Isi, niwe niho muzo kwegeranywa"
  67,25,"Nabo bavuga bati:- niryari iryo sango nimwaba mu vugisha ukuri"
  67,26,"Vuga uti :- ubumenyi bwavyo buri ku Mana, kandi mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi umutuza gusa n’uwuba sobanurira"
  67,27,"Mugabo mugihe bazo kibonera kiri hafi, amaso y’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri azo mara mara hanyuma havurwe hati:- ibi nivyo mwahora musaba"
  67,28,"Vuga uti:- ni mumbwire yuko Imana niya mponya jewe, hamwe nabo turi kumwe, canke itugiriye impuhwe zayo, none ni nde azoba kingira abo bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ibihano vy’Imana bibabaza"
  67,29,"Vuga uti:- Imana niyo nyene impuhwe nyinshi twebwe tuyemera n’ukuyizera, nubu vuba muzo menya uwuri m’ubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  67,30,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe mubona gute nkiyo amazi yanyu yoba yibijwe mu kuzimu, none ni nde yobazanira amazi meza y’isoko"
  68,1,"Nuun, (Insiguro y’iyi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwayo bwose n’Imana yonyene gusa). Kandi ndarahiye kw’ikaramu hamwe nivyo bandikisha ko"
  68,2,"No kumigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, wewe nturi umusazi"
  68,3,Mu vy’ukuri wewe urafise impembo idahera
  68,4,Kandi ntankeka wewe urafise ingeso nziza cane
  68,5,"Rero ubu vuba uzo bona, nabo nyene bazobona"
  68,6,Ni nde afise ibisazi muri mwebwe
  68,7,"Mu vy’ukuri umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’uwazimiye munzira yiwe, kandi irabazi cane abarongotse"
  68,8,Rero ntuba gamburukire abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri
  68,9,Bagomba yuko wo borohereza nabo bakorohererwa
  68,10,Kandi ntugamburukire uwurahira cane nawe ari mu bantu batishoboye
  68,11,Umuvuzi w’insaku agenda asasagaza urwanko mu bantu
  68,12,"Akingira imigisha nugu hemukira ibiremwa nkawe, n’uguhakana Imana yiwe"
  68,13,"Nyene\tumutima\tukomeye,\tkuri\tivyo\tvyose\tni\tnk’ikintu\tcashinguwe ahantu mugabo ntigishingurwe neza"
  68,14,Kubera yuko afise amatungo n’ibibondo
  68,15,"Mugihe\tasomewe\tamajambo\tyacu\tmatagtifu\tavuga\tati:-\taya\tniya majambo y’ububeshi bw’abantu ba kera"
  68,16,Tuzo mushira ko inkovu kw’izuru ryiwe
  68,17,"Mu vy’ukuri abo bantu tuzobaha ibibazo nkuko twashize ko ibibazo kubari bafise imirima, mugihe barahira yuko bazo kwimbura kuri iyo mirima nihashika mu gitondo"
  68,18,Kandi ntibabwiye n’umukene numwe
  68,19,Rero warashikiwe n’ivyago bivuye ku Muremyi wabo nabo basinziriye
  68,20,Uwo murima uba nk’uwahiye
  68,21,Bukeye bara hamagarana
  68,22,"Yuko\tbogenda\thakiri\tkare\tku\tmurima\twanyu\tnimwaba\tmushaka kwimbura"
  68,23,Baragiye bongorerana
  68,24,Yuko uno musi ata mukene yinjira
  68,25,"Baragenda mugitondo biyumvira yuko bafise ububasha\tbw’ukuba buza ba bakene"
  68,26,"Mugihe\tbabona\twa\tmurima\tbaciye\tbavuga\tbati:-\tntankeka\ttwebwe twazimiye"
  68,27,Canke batwankiye
  68,28,"Umwe mubagira neza yavuze ati:- mbega sinaba bwiye yuko mu garuka ku Muremyi wanyu mu musabe ikigongwe"
  68,29,"Nabo ba mwishura bati:- iteka ni ry’Umuremyi wacu, mu vy’ukuri twara hemukiye imitima yacu"
  68,30,Baca bahangana n’abandi baterana imyikomo
  68,31,"Bavuga\tbati:-\turu\tn’uruhombo\trwacu,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\ttwari\ttwararenze imbibe z’Imana"
  68,32,"Nkumbure\tUmuremyi\twacu\tazo\tduhindurira\tuwundi\tmurima\tmwiza gusumba uwu, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turiyegereje ku Muremyi wacu"
  68,33,"Uku\tniko\tbiba\tibihano\tvy’Umuremyi\twawe,\tn’ibihano\tvy’umusi w’imperuka ni bininiya cane gusumba nkiyo bobi menya"
  68,34,"Mu vy’ukuri abagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri, bazoba bafise ijuru rifise imigisha y’Umuremyi wabo"
  68,35,Mbega tubagire abagamburutsi nk’abononyi
  68,36,"Mbega mubaye gute, muca intahe gute"
  68,37,Canke murafise igitabu musomamwo
  68,38,Yuko muzoronka ivyo mwipfuza
  68,39,Canke murafise amasezerano kuri twebwe azoguma ho kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka yuko muzoronka ivyo mwiganzira
  68,40,"N’ubabaze muti :- ni nde muribo yofata ingwati kuri ibi vyose"
  68,41,"Canke barafise abo bacuditse hamwe, rero nibabazane abo bacuditse hamwe niba bavugisha ukuri kwama"
  68,42,"Kuri uwo musi hazoba ibihano bikaze cane, bazo hamagarwa gupfukama bashira imitwe yabo hasi, mugabo ntibazo shobora"
  68,43,"Amaso yabo azoba araba hasi, agahinda nako kabapfuke, mu vy’ukuri bahora bahamagarwa gupfukama bashire imitwe yabo hasi mugihe bari mubantu beranda"
  68,44,"Nundeke hamwe n’abahakana ibi biganiro, tuzoba kwega buhoro buhoro mubihano vyacu ku hantu batazi"
  68,45,"Ndabahaye umwanya, mu vy’ukuri ububasha bwanje bura komeye cane"
  68,46,Canke urabasaba impembo nabo bakarengerwa nayo magarama
  68,47,Canke kuribo hariho ubumenyi bw’amabanga bahawe bw’intumwa z’Imana bandika
  68,48,"Rero n’utenyenye kw’itegeko ry’Umuremyi wawe, kandi ntube nk’uwamizwe n’ifi, mugihe yatabaza Imana yiwe nawe ageramiwe nabi cane"
  68,49,"Iyo adashikirwa n’imigisha ivuye ku Muremyi wiwe, ntankeka yari gutabwa ku nkengera y’ikiyaga nawe atabwa ko umwikomo"
  68,50,Mugabo Umuremyi wiwe niwe yamugenye nukumugira mu bantu b’intungane
  68,51,"Nayo ba bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, baregereza kuguhuvya n’amaso yabo, mugihe bumvise ubutumwa bwawe nuguca bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri uyu muntu n’umusazi"
  68,52,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ari icibutso kubantu bose
  69,1,Icabaye c’ukuri
  69,2,Nico cabaye c’ukuri n’igiki
  69,3,N’igiki kizo kumenyesha ico kintu cabaye c’ukuri
  69,4,Bene Thamudu na bene Aadi barahakanye umusi w’umuhero w’isi
  69,5,Rero abo bene Thamudu barahonejwe kuvyago bininiya cane
  69,6,Nayo bene Aadi barahonejwe n’igihuhusi gikaze cane kida kingirwa
  69,7,"Wabatwaye amajoro indwi n’imitaga umunani, ubwo nyene uda hengeshanije, ugasanga abantu baguye igihumure nkakumwe kw’ibishitsi vy’imitende vyaguye hasi bimeze nk’imiroha"
  69,8,Mbega wabonye umwe muribo yasigaye
  69,9,"Na Fir’auni hamwe n’abamyeho imbere yiwe nabo mubisagara vyahinduwe, nabone baragize amakosa"
  69,10,Bariyonkora kuntumwa z’Umuremyi wabo ari naho yabafata kunguvu zitabaho
  69,11,"Mugihe umwuzurire w’amazi washika, twebwe twarabadugije tuburiza muri ico kigenda aribwo bwato"
  69,12,"Kugira ngo kibe icibutso kuri mwebwe, n’ugutwi kwumva kwumvire ho"
  69,13,N’igihe hazovuzwa inzamba izovuzwa rimwe gusa
  69,14,N’Isi hamwe n’Imisozi bizo kurwaho n’ugusenyurwa rimwe gusa
  69,15,Kuri uwo musi ibizoba bizoba vyamaze kuba
  69,16,"N’amajuru\tazo\tmanyagurika,\trero\tkuri\tuwo\tmusi\tAmajuru\tazoba ahoyahoya cane"
  69,17,"N’Abamarayika\tbazoba\tbari\thambavu\tyayo\tmajuru\tn’Abamarayika b’ubwoko umunani nibo bazorerura inyegamo y’iteka y’Umuremyi wawe"
  69,18,Kuri uwo musi mwese muzo kwerekwa naho hatazo nyegezwa amabanga yanyu yose
  69,19,"Rero\tuwuzo\thabwa\tigitabu\tc’ibikorwa\tvyiwe\tmu\tkuboko\tkwiwe kw’iburyo azovuga n’akamwemwe kenshi ati:- ni musome igitabu canje"
  69,20,Mu vy’ukuri ndazi yuko nzohabwa ibiharuro vyanje
  69,21,Nawe azoba ari mu buzima bw’akanyamuneza ntangere
  69,22,Mw’ijuru ritagatifu
  69,23,Ivyamwa bigerekeranye kubindi bizoba hafi kuribo
  69,24,"Nimufungure muteko munywe n’umunezero ntangere, kubera ibikorwa mwagize muri iyo misi yahera"
  69,25,"Mugabo\tuwuzohabwa\tigitabu\tciwe\tmukuboko\tkwiwe\tkw’ibubamfu azovuga ati :- Yo! Iyo ntohawe iki gitabu canje"
  69,26,Kandi sinari kumenya ikihe giharuro canje
  69,27,Iyo urupfu rumarira ivyanje vyose
  69,28,Amatungo yanje ntaco yamariye
  69,29,Ubutegetsi bwanje bwara ntakaranye
  69,30,Ni mumufate mumushire ko iminyororo
  69,31,Hanyuma mumujugunyire mumuriro udahera
  69,32,Kandi abe yaboshwe n’umunyororo ufise uburebure bw’imetero mirongo indwi muce mu mwinjiza yo
  69,33,Mu vy’ukuri ntiyigeze yemera Imana yiwe ntagatifu
  69,34,Kandi ntiya himiriza abandi kugira ngo arishe abakene
  69,35,Rero uno musi ngaha ntamukunzi muhire n’umwe afise
  69,36,Nta n’ibifungurwa afise atari amazi y’amashira gusa
  69,37,Ntiba gufungura ivyo bifungurwa atari abanya vyaha
  69,38,Rero ndarahiye kubintu mubona
  69,39,N’ivyo mutabona
  69,40,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taka\tn’akamo\tkazanywe\tn’intumwa\ty’Imana\tifise\titeka rininiya cane"
  69,41,"Kandi s’imvugo y’umwanditsi w’amajambo y’ubuhizi nkuko mu bivuga, nani bakeyi cane muyemera"
  69,42,"Kandi\ts’amajambo\ty’umurozi\tnkuko\tmubivuga,\tni\tgakeyi\tcane\tkuri mwebwe kugira ngo mushobore kwemera ubu butumwa"
  69,43,N’imanurwa rivuye ku Muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  69,44,Iyo yiyadukiza kuri twebwe bimwe mu majambo asanzwe gusa
  69,45,Ntankeka twebwe twari kumu cakira n’ukuboko kw’iburyo
  69,46,Kandi mu vy’ukuri twari kumuca umutsi mukuru w’umutima wiwe
  69,47,Kandi nta n’umwe muri mwebwe yari kutubuza mukuta mufata
  69,48,Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu n’ubutumwa ku bantu bagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri
  69,49,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\tturazi\tneza\tyuko\tmuri\tmwebwe\tharimwo abahakanyi"
  69,50,Uzoba ari umubabaro ku bantu batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  69,51,Mu vy’ukuri uku n’ukuri nyakuri
  69,52,"Rero n’uninahaze izina ry’Umuremyi wawe ariwe mukuru. Igisomwa c’Ukuduga.\tIkigabane\tca (29). Camanukiye IMakkat. Gifise imirongo"
  70,1,Uwabajije abaza kubijanye n’ibihano bizoba
  70,2,Kubera abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bada shobora kuwu hagarika uwo musi
  70,3,Bivuye ku Mana nyene iteka rikuru cane
  70,4,Abamarayika hamwe n’imitima y’abantu bose yama iduga iwe k’umusi waho ikiringo cayo ari imyaka ibihumbi mirongo itanu
  70,5,Rero ni wigumye kuwigumya neza
  70,6,Mu vy’ukuri uwo musi w’umuhero w’isi bo bawubona yuko uri kure cane
  70,7,Natwe tuwubona yuko uri hafi cane
  70,8,Umusi amajuru azoba nk’ubutare bw’umujumpu bwashaye cane
  70,9,N’Imisozi ikazoba nk’isufi zaguruwe ziri mukirere
  70,10,N’umugenzi ntazo baza mugenzi wiwe
  70,11,Naho bogirwa ngo babonane nuwuri mumakosa azokwipfuza yuko yo kwikombora n’ibihano vy’uwo musi w’umuhero w’Isi mu gutanga ibibondo vyiwe
  70,12,N’umukenyezi wiwe hamwe na bene wabo
  70,13,N’abagenzi biwe bamukikuje kumpande zose
  70,14,N’ibiri kw’isi vyose hanyuma arokoke
  70,15,"Mugabo sivyo, mu vy’ukuri uwo n’umuriro waka neza cane"
  70,16,Ubabura urukoba rw’umubiri rimwe na rimwe
  70,17,"Uzo\thamagara\tkuwahindukije\tumugongo\twiwe\tnuguhindukira\tmu kutitaho inyigisho z’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani"
  70,18,N’uwegeranije amatungo yiwe hanyuma akayaziganya
  70,19,Mu vy’ukuri umuntu yaremwe n’igihababu cinshi
  70,20,Mugihe ashikiwe n’ishari niho aca asimbwa n’umutima
  70,21,Ashikiwe n’amahirwe aca yigungira ko
  70,22,Dukuye mwo abasenga Imana yabo y’ukuri
  70,23,N’abatsimbataza amasengesho yabo
  70,24,N’abafise mu matungo yabo harimwo igice cabo kizwi neza
  70,25,Kubera uwasavye n’uwigumya mu kudasega
  70,26,N’abemera umusi w’impembo
  70,27,N’abatinya ibihano vy’Umuremyi wabo
  70,28,Mu vy’ukuri ibihano vy’Umuremyi wabo si ivyu kurokoka kw’umuntu w’umunyavyaha
  70,29,N’abapfuka ibitsina vyabo
  70,30,"Dukuye mwo abakenyezi babo canke bamwe batunzwe bari mu minwe yabo y’iburyo, abo nibo badatabwako umwikomo"
  70,31,"Mugabo abipfuza kuronka ibitari ibi, abo nibo barenga imbibe zagenywe n’Imana"
  70,32,Naba ziganya ivyabo hamwe n’amasezerano yabo
  70,33,Naba hagaze neza mukuba ivyabona vyabo
  70,34,Naba bunga bunga amasengesho yabo
  70,35,Abo nibo bazoba bari mu mirima bafise urupfasoni ntangere
  70,36,Bafise iki bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri mugihe bagukanuriye amaso yabo gusa
  70,37,Imirwi y’abantu n’iyindi izoba iri k’uruhande rw’iburyo n’ibubamfu
  70,38,Mbega umwe wese muribo yizeye yuko azo kwinjizwa muri iryo juru ry’imigisha
  70,39,"Oya! Sivyo, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twabaremye muvyo bazi"
  70,40,Rero ndarahiye ku Muremyi wo m’ubuseruko bwose no mu burengero bwose yuko twebwe tubishoboye
  70,41,"Kubahindura abari intungane gusumba abahahora, natwe ntitunaniwe"
  70,42,"Rero\tnimubareke\tbiyagire\tayamuhe\tbateko\tbafyinate,\tkugeza\tnaho bazobona umusi wabo bemerewe"
  70,43,Umusi bazova mu ntatemwa zabo ningoga na ningoga nkuko birukira aho basiganirwa ho
  70,44,"Amaso yabo azoba yunamye apfutswe n’ibimaramare, uwo niwo musi bahora bemererwa"
  71,1,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twararungitse intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) ku bantu biwe, yuko yobatuza imbere yuko bashikirwa n’ibihano bibabaza cane"
  71,2,"Nawe\tavuga\tati:-\temwe\tbantu\tbanje,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tjewe\tndi\tuwutuza mboneka neza kuri mwebwe"
  71,3,"Yuko mwosenga Imana yanyu y’ukuri, muyigamburukire kandi munyubahe"
  71,4,"Izoba girira ikigongwe kubicumuro vyanyu, kandi izoba tebereza kugeza k’umwanya wagenewe, mu vy’ukuri naho impanuka yoturuka ku Mana ntikingirwa nk’iyo mwobimenya"
  71,5,"Intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) yavuze iti:- ewe Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri abantu banje jewe nabashikirije ubutumwa ijoro n’umutaga"
  71,6,Mugabo ubutumwa bwanje nta nakimwe bwongereje atari uku mpunga gusa
  71,7,"Nuko naba hamagara kugira ngo ubagirire ikigongwe, baca baziba amatwi yabo bakoresheje intoke zabo, n’ukwipfuka impuzu zabo hose, baca bongereza babandanya guhakana n’ukwishima kwinshi cane"
  71,8,Kandi jewe naraba hamagaye k’umugaragaro
  71,9,"Hanyuma ndabatera akamo k’ijwi rirerire, kandi ndavugana nabo mu mwiherero"
  71,10,"Ndababwira nti:- ni musabe ikigongwe ku Muremyi wanyu, mu vy’ukuri niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi gusumba"
  71,11,Izoba zanira ibicu bisesa gurika imvura nyinshi cane
  71,12,"Kandi izobaha amatungo hamwe n’ibibondo, kandi izobaha n’imirima, kandi ibagirire n’inzuzi"
  71,13,"Mubaye gute, nta rupfasoni mugirira Imana"
  71,14,Mugihe ariyo yabaremye muri ubu buryo n’ubundi
  71,15,"Mbega\tnti\tmubona\tingene\tImana\tyaremye\tAmajuru\tuko\tari\tindwi agerekeranye kuyandi"
  71,16,"N’ukugira Ukwezi muri kwo kube ari umuco, n’ukugira Izuba kuba ari itara"
  71,17,N’Imana yaraba nagishije kw’isi ibiterwa
  71,18,Hanyuma izoba subiza muri yo kandi izo bakuramwo
  71,19,N’Imana yarabagiriye Isi kuba ikintu ciza mwasasiwe
  71,20,Kugira ngo mugire kuriyo mu nzira z’agutse
  71,21,"Intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) yavuze iti:- Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri abo bantu banje biyonkoye kuri jewe, kandi bakurikiye abafise amatungo yabo n’ibibondo vyabo ata kindi babongereje atari uruhombo gusa"
  71,22,Baca bagira ingeso niniya z’uguta idini
  71,23,"N’abababwiye aba bakurikiye bati:- ntimusige Imana zanyu canke ntimusige uwitwa Waddan hamwe na Suwa’a, na Yaghutha na Yauqa na Nas’raa"
  71,24,"Nabo bakaba baratakaje abantu benshi, rero ntubongereze aba hemukiye imitima y’abo atari ukuzimirira kure"
  71,25,"Rero kubera amakosa yabo baciye bibizwa mumazi n’ukwinjizwa mu muriro udahera, kandi ntiba ronse ababa tabara imbere y’Imana"
  71,26,"N’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) yagumye abandanya avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, ntusige uwariwe wese kuri iy’Isi muri abo bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  71,27,"Mu vy’ukuri niwaba siga abo bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bazo zimiza abantu bawe barongotse, kandi ntibazo kwibaruka atari ibibondo bibi cane vy’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri nkuko kwabo"
  71,28,"Muremyi wanje, jewe n’ungirire ikigongwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banje, hamwe n’uwinjiye munzu yanje nawe ari umu Isilamu, hamwe naba Isilamu b’abagabo hamwe naba Isilamu kazi, kandi ntu bongereze abahemukiye imitima yabo atari ukuba honya gusa"
  72,1,"Vuga uti:- naramenyeshejwe kuri jewe yuko umurwi umwe w’ibisigo wumvise amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani uca uvuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri twumvise amajambo ya Qur’ani y’igitangaza"
  72,2,"Irongora k’uburongozi, kuri ivyo natwe turayemeye kandi ntituzo kwigera tugereranya Imana n’ikindi kintu hamwe n’Umuremyi wacu"
  72,3,Kandi mu vy’ukuri iteka ry’Umuremyi wacu riratewe iteka rihagije cane kuko itigeze yigirira umukenyezi canke ikibondo
  72,4,Mu vy’ukuri abadafise ubwenge muri twebwe bamye bavuga amajambo yarengeje urugero hejuru y’Imana
  72,5,Natwe twamye twiyumvira yuko abantu hamwe n’ibisigo batazo besha hejuru y’Imana
  72,6,"Mu vy’ukuri hari abagabo mubiremwa vy’Imana bikingira kubagabo b’ibisigo, kuri ivyo babongereza ingorane zidasanzwe"
  72,7,Mu vy’ukuri biketse nkuko mwiketse mwebwe yuko Imana itazo zana iyindi ntumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose
  72,8,Natwe twarakoze kumajuru tuyabona acungerewe n’abafise inguvu hamwe n’inyenyeri zisa yangana
  72,9,Mu vy’ukuri twahora twicara mu nyubakwa kugira ngo twumvirize mugabo uwashaka kwumviriza ubwo nyene yahasanga ibishirira vy’umucanwa bimu rorereye
  72,10,"Natwe ntavyo twari tuzi yuko bashakirwa ishari bamwe baba ngaha kw’isi, canke Umuremyi wabo abashakira uburokoke"
  72,11,"Mu vy’ukuri muri twebwe harimwo abantu beza n’abandi muri twebwe bateye ukundi, rero turi mu nzira zitandukanye"
  72,12,Natwe twari tuzi yuko tudashobora gutsinda Imana kuri iy’Isi kandi tudashobora kumwiyaka ngo twiruke
  72,13,Natwe mugihe twumva ubwo burokoke twaciye tubwemera rero uwemeye Umuremyi wiwe ntazotinya kuzimbwa canke kwegekwako ibicumuro vy’uwundi muntu
  72,14,Natwe harimwo bamwe muri twebwe bemeye kuba aba Isilamu hakaba n’abandi muri twebwe baguma bajuragirika bamaze kuba aba Isilamu abo nibo barondeye uburokoke
  72,15,N’abajuragirika abo bazoba ari inkwi zo mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  72,16,Iyo bafata nka nkama inzira igororotse twari kuba nywesha amazi menshi
  72,17,"Kugira\tngo\ttubagerageze\tkuri\tivyo\tvyose\tn’uwutitaho\tmu\tkwibuka Umuremyi wiwe, izomu sunika mubihano bigoye cane"
  72,18,"Mu vy’ukuri amasengero yose nay’Imana, rero ntimusenge uwariwe wese hamwe n’Imana y’ukuri"
  72,19,Mu vy’ukuri umushumvyi w’Imana Muhammadi (aui) igihe yahagarara asaba Umuremyi wiwe bari hafi yukumurwako
  72,20,"Vuga uti:- Jewe nsenga Umuremyi wanje gusa, kandi sinda mugereranya n’ibindi bintu"
  72,21,"Vuga\tuti:-\tjewe\tsindabaganza\tkugira\tngo\tndabagirire\tinabi,\tcanke kubarongora"
  72,22,"Vuga\tuti:-\tntankeka\tntan’umwe\tashobora\tkunkingira\tn’Imana,\tkandi sinzoronka ibwicaro bw’amahoro atari kuriyo yonyene gusa"
  72,23,"Mugabo mugushikiriza ubutumwa buvuye ku Mana hamwe n’amategeko yayo, hamwe n’abazokwiyonjorora ku Mana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa yayo ntankeka bazoronswa umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu bazowubamwo mu buzima bwabo bwose"
  72,24,"Kugeza aho bazobonera ivyo bemerewe, niho bazotahura uwariwe afise umufasha uhoya hoya n’uwufise igitigiri gitoyi"
  72,25,"Vuga uti:- sindabizi yuko ivyo mwemerewe biri hafi canke Umuremyi wanje azo biha ikiringo kirekire"
  72,26,"Niyo nyene ubumenyi bw’amabanga yose, kandi ntiyereka uwariwe wese amabanga yayo"
  72,27,"Dukuye mwo intumwa yayo yemereye, uyo niyo yashiriye ho abamu kingira bari imbere yiwe n’inyuma yiwe"
  72,28,"Kugira ngo atahure yuko bashikanye ubutumwa bw’umuremyi wabo, n’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo bafise vyose, kandi niyo yafashe nka nkama igitigiri c’ibintu vyose"
  73,1,Wewe wipfutse amahuzu
  73,2,Nuhagarare mw’ijoro mugabo mu mwanya mutoyi gusa
  73,3,Igice c’iryo joro canke ugabanye gatoyi
  73,4,"Canke wongerezeko gatoyi, hanyuma usome iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu nkuko bitegetswe"
  73,5,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzo kumanurira imvugo iremereye cane
  73,6,Mu vy’ukuri ukwikangura mw’ijoro n’ukugira ibisabisho bihurana neza n’umushaha hamwe n’amajambo yayo ahumuriza cane
  73,7,Mu vy’ukuri k’umurango urafise ibikorwa vyinshi cane
  73,8,Nurivuge izina ry’Umuremyi wawe kandi witeho kuriyo bimwe vy’ukuri
  73,9,"Umuremyi\tw’ubuseruko\tnuburengera\tzuba,\tntayindi\tisengwa\tatariyo yonyene gusa, rero n’uyigire kuba ariyo igukingiye"
  73,10,"Ni\twigumye kuri ivyo vyose bavuga abo bahakanyi b’Imana,\tkandi ubikure ko ube kure yabo n’amahoro"
  73,11,"N’undeke\tjewe\thamwe\tnabo\tbahakanyi\tbaronse\tamahirwe,\thanyuma ubahe ikiringo kigufiya gusa"
  73,12,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turafise ibihano hamwe n’umuriro udahera waka cane
  73,13,N’ibifungurwa biniga mu muhogo hamwe n’ibihano bibabaza cane
  73,14,"K’umusi\twaho\tIsi\thamwe\tn’Imisozi\tizo\tnyiganzwa,\tn’Imisozi\tikazoba nk’iyegeranijwe nk’umusenyi udafadika"
  73,15,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraba zaniye intumwa y’Imana y’icabona kuri mwebwe, nkuko twamutwariye intumwa y’Imana kwa Fir’auni"
  73,16,"Mugabo Fir’auni yariyonkoye kuntumwa y’Imana\tnatwe tura muhana ibihano bininiya cane"
  73,17,"Mwebwe nimwa hakana, mushobora gute kwikingira n’ivyago vy’umusi uzogira ibibondo kuba banaze imvi nk’abatama"
  73,18,"Amajuru azo satagurika kuri uwo musi, amasezerano yayo azo kurikizwa atagisivya"
  73,19,"Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu n’ubutumwa bw’Imana, rero uwushaka azo kwigirira inzira yiwe nziza ku Muremyi wiwe"
  73,20,"Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi buhagije yuko wewe uhagarara hafi y’ibice bibiri vy’ica gatatu c’ijoro, canke igice cayo n’uwundi mwanya ugahagarara kugice cica gatatu, na bamwe mu bantu muri kumwe nabo bagira nk’ibi hamwe na wewe, n’Imana niyo itegura neza ukugene uburebure bw’ijoro n’umutaga bungana, kandi niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije yuko udashobora kugira ivyo, ikaba yarabagiriye ikigongwe kuri ivyo, rero ni musome ibiba yabaye kiborohereye kuri mwebwe mu majambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani, kuko irafise ubumenyi yuko bamwe muri mwebwe bazoba bakitswe n’amagara, abandi nabo bazoba bari mu rugendo ngaha kw’Isi barondera imigisha y’Imana, n’abandi nabo barwana mu nzira y’Imana, rero ni musome kubi boroheye muri ico gitabu gitagatifu, c’Imana hanyuma muhagarike amasengesho yanyu n’ugutanga imperezwa zanyu, hanyuma mubegurire Imana ikimanyu ciza, n’ineza iyariyo yose muzo yitanguza kubera imitima yanyu muzoyisanga ku Mana ari nziza cane, kandi ifise imigisha mininiya cane, kandi musabe ikigongwe ku Mana yanyu, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise imbabazi nyinshi cane n’impuhwe zihagije"
  74,1,Wewe wipfutse amahuzu
  74,2,Haguruka utuze abantu
  74,3,Uninahaze Umuremyi wawe
  74,4,Usukure n’impuzu zawe
  74,5,N’amabi yose ntuyiteho
  74,6,"Kandi\tntugire\tineza\tkubiremwa\tkugira\tngo\turonke\tumusesekara w’amaronko ngaha kw’isi"
  74,7,"Kubera Umuremyi wawe, wewe niwigumye gusa"
  74,8,Niha vuzwa inzamba y’umuhero w’isi
  74,9,Kuri uwo musi uzoba ari umusi uhambaye cane
  74,10,"Kubahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, uwo musi ntuzoba woroshe kuribo namba"
  74,11,Jewe n’undeke hamwe nuwo niremeye jewe nyene
  74,12,Ndamuhezagire aronke amatungo menshi
  74,13,N’ibibondo biboneka ahariho hose
  74,14,Ndamugirira ibintu vyiwe neza cane
  74,15,Hanyuma yizera yuko nzomwongereza
  74,16,Oya! Mu vy’ukuri yahora ahakana amajambo yacu meranda
  74,17,Rero nzo muhana n’ibihano bininiya cane
  74,18,Mu vy’ukuri yariyumviriye n’ugupima
  74,19,"Arahonywa, none ni gute yateguye mugutyoza iyi Qur’ani"
  74,20,"Kandi yarahonejwe, none ni gute yateguye mugutyoza iyi Qur’ani"
  74,21,Hanyuma yaritegereje
  74,22,Hanyuma arazinga mumaso yiwe kugeza naho haboneka iminkanyari
  74,23,Hanyuma ukuri aguha umugongo wiwe n’ukwishima cane
  74,24,"N’ukuvuga ati:- ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari uburozi bwabuwe"
  74,25,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari amajambo y’umuntu asanzwe
  74,26,Ubu vuba nzomuta mu muriro udahera
  74,27,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo muriro udahera
  74,28,Udasigaza nico usigaza
  74,29,Uwo muriro nuwu babura urukoba rimwe na rimwe
  74,30,Hejuru yuwo muriro udahera hariho abawucungera bashika kw’icumi n’icenda
  74,31,"Ntitwashizeho abacungera uwo muriro udahera atari abamarayika, kandi ntitwagize igitigiri cabo cumi n’icenda atari uko ari ikibazo kuri barya bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri kugira ngo bashirwe n’abahawe ibitabu imbere yanyu, n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bagumane ukwemera kwabo, kandi ntibagire amakenga bamwe bahawe igitabu imbere yanyu canke aba Isilamu n’abazoba bafise indwara mu mitima yabo hamwe n’abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baze bavuge bati:- Imana yashatse kugira iki kuri kano karorero? Uku rero niko Imana ireka umuntu akazimira kuwo yishakiye n’ukurongora uwo yishakiye, kandi nta numwe afise ubumenyi bw’ukumenya ingabo z’Umuremyi wawe atariyo yonyene gusa, kandi ntivyari kuba atari ikimenyetso kubiremwa vyose"
  74,32,Sivyo none ? Ndarahiye k’ukwezi
  74,33,N’Ijoro rikeye
  74,34,No mugitondo hakeye
  74,35,Mu vy’ukuri uwo muriro udahera n’umwe mungorane niniya zihambaye cane
  74,36,N’igabisho ku bantu
  74,37,K’uwushaka muri mwebwe n’atanguze kuja imbere canke aje inyuma
  74,38,"Umutima\tw’umwumwe\twese\tuzo\tkwugaranirwa\tmu\tmuriro\tudahera kubera ibikorwa bibi wakoze"
  74,39,Dukuye mwo abantu b’iburyo
  74,40,Abo bantu bazoba mu mirima babazanya
  74,41,Kubera abantu babi
  74,42,N’ikintu nyabaki cabatwaye mu muriro udahera
  74,43,"Bazo vuga bati:- ntitwari mu bantu bahora basenga"
  74,44,Kandi ntitwahora duha abakene ibifungugwa
  74,45,Kandi twahora twibira mu bicumuro hamwe n’abahora bibira
  74,46,Kandi twahora duhakana yuko ata musi w’uguciribwa imanza
  74,47,Kugeza n’aho dushikirwa n’urupfu
  74,48,Ntaco bizofasha uko gusaba kw’abasabira abaribo bose
  74,49,Mbega bafise iki ? Ntibitaho kuri rino tuza
  74,50,Nkuko umengo n’indogobwe zigenda ningoga na ningoga
  74,51,Ziruka nk’intare
  74,52,"Umwe wese muribo\tagomba yuko ahabwa impapuro zizoba zanditswe ko"
  74,53,Oya! kuri bo ntibatinya umuhero w’Isi
  74,54,"Oya ! Si uko, mu vy’ukuri ubwo n’ubwibutso"
  74,55,Rero uwushaka azokwibuka
  74,56,"Ntibazo kwibuka atari uko Imana yabishatse, kuko niyo ikwiwe gutinywa n’ukugira imbabazi"
  75,1,Ndarahiye k’umusi w’umuhero w’isi
  75,2,Kandi ndarahiye k’umutima widoga
  75,3,Yibaza umuntu yuko twebwe tutazo kwegeranya amagufa yiwe
  75,4,"Kubera iki, twebwe turashoboye kuringaniza amasonga y’intoke ziwe"
  75,5,Mugabo umuntu ashaka gusa guhakana ibiri imbere yiwe gusa
  75,6,Akabaza nk’agahemo uwo musi w’umuhero w’Isi uzobera
  75,7,N’umusi ijisho ry’umuntu rizobona nk’umuravyo
  75,8,N’ukwezi mugihe kuzo fatwa
  75,9,N’Izuba hamwe n’Ukwezi bizo huzwa ariko gufatwa
  75,10,"Umuntu azo vuga kuri uwo musi ati:- ni uruhe ruhande rw’ukwirukira"
  75,11,Oya! Nta hantu hukwirukira
  75,12,Kuri uwo musi ingaruka ya vyose ni ku Muremyi wawe gusa
  75,13,"Kuri uwo musi umuntu azobwirwa kuvyo yagize aho hambere, hamwe nivyo yagize mu nyuma yaho"
  75,14,Ahubwo umuntu niwe cabona c’umutima wiwe
  75,15,Naho atanga ivyitwazo vyiwe vy’ububeshi
  75,16,Ntunyiganze ururimi rwawe mu kuru girira ivyihutirwa bimanuka
  75,17,Mu vy’ukuri ni kuri twebwe kuwegeranya n’ukuwigisha
  75,18,"Mugihe twebwe tugusomera, wewe n’ukurikize uko gusomwa kwavyo"
  75,19,Hanyuma ni hejuru yacu kubikwereka
  75,20,"Sivyo none, ahubwo mwebwe nimwe mukunda ubuzima bwaha kw’isi"
  75,21,N’ukureka ubuzima bwo mw’ijuru
  75,22,Amaso y’abandi kuri uwo musi azoba asayangana
  75,23,Araba Umuremyi wabo
  75,24,N’ayandi maso kuri uwo musi azo kwizinga
  75,25,Azomenya yuko azoshikirwa n’ivyago bivuna agatiri gongo
  75,26,Sivyo none! Uku mugira mugihe umutima uzoshika kumagufa y’ibitugu vyabo
  75,27,"Hazovurwa hati :- ni nde ashobora kuvura uyu murwayi"
  75,28,Nawe akamenya yuko ari umwanya w’urupfu
  75,29,Mugihe hazokurikizwa umurundi k’uwundi
  75,30,"Kuri uwo musi n’ugucungerwa gusa, n’ukujanwa k’Umuremyi wawe"
  75,31,Ntiyemeye canke ntiyasenze
  75,32,Ahubwo yarahakanye n’ugusubira inyuma
  75,33,Hanyuma yaragiye ku bantu biwe nawe yijanda jandira
  75,34,"Uramaze gushikirwa n’ibihano vy’Imana, mbega biramaze kugushikira"
  75,35,"Hanyuma\turamaze\tgushikirwa\tn’ibihano\tvy’Imana,\tmbega\tbiramaze kugushikira"
  75,36,Mbega wiyumvira yuko umuntu azorekwa gutya nyene agende akagirire
  75,37,Mbega ntiyari ima ry’intanga ryatewe
  75,38,"Hanyuma riba ikimanyu c’amaraso, hanyuma Imana ira murema nuku muringaniza ari umuntu akwiye"
  75,39,"Hanyuma imugira impande zibiri, z’ukuba umugabo n’umugore"
  75,40,"Mbega\tntiyari\tkuba\tuyo\tariwe\tnyene\tubushobozi\tbw’ukuzura abashengeye bose"
  76,1,Mu vy’ukuri ikiremwa muntu carahitiwe n’umwanya muremure w’imyaka myinshi kita raba ikintu na kimwe kivurwa kuri we
  76,2,"Mu vy’ukuri twaremye umuntu biturutse kumbuto y’ubuzima ivanzwe ni y’umugabo hamwe ni y’umugore, kugira ngo tumugirire ibibazo, kuri ivyo tumugira uwumva n’ukubona"
  76,3,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twara murongoye mu nzira zose azoba arimwo aba uwushima canke uwuhakana
  76,4,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaraba teguriye abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, iminyororo hamwe n’imigozi y’umuriro ukaze cane"
  76,5,Mu vy’ukuri abantu beranda bazonywa ibinyobwa bivanzwe mwo n’akamoto kitiriwe Kafuri
  76,6,"Iyo\tKafuri\tn’umwonga\tuzonywa\tmwo\tabantu\tberanda\tb’Imana\tukazo shunguruka mwo amazi afise ishunguruka ryiza nkuko bipfuza"
  76,7,Abo bantu ni bamwe bakwijije ibikenewe vyabo n’ugutinya umusi w’ishari ryawo uzo kwiragira hose
  76,8,"Naba gaburira ibi fungurwa aboro hamwe n’impfuvyi hamwe n’imbohe, mugihe nabo ku bwabo bakunda ivyo bifungurwa"
  76,9,"Mu mitima yabo bavuga bati:- tuba risha ibi bifungurwa kugushaka impuhwe z’Imana gusa, kuko ntidushaka kuri mwebwe impembo iyariyo yose canke yuko mwodushimira"
  76,10,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe dutinya ku Muremyi wacu uwo musi w’ingorane n’uburuhe
  76,11,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tImana\tizoba\tkingira\tn’ishari\tryuwo\tmusi\tn’ukuba\thuza n’imigisha yayo hamwe n’akanya muneza ntangere"
  76,12,"Imana\tizo\tbaha\takaganuke\tk’imirima\tyo\tmw’ijuru\thamwe\tn’impuzu zihwahutse kubera ukwigumya kwabo"
  76,13,"Iyo mw’ijuru bazo kwegamira kunyegamo z’iteka, nti bazobona yo izuba rikaze cane , canke imbeho ikaze cane kuribo"
  76,14,"N’ibitutu\tvyayo\tbizoba\tbiri\thafi\tcane\tkuri\tbo,\thamwe\tn’ivyamwa vyegeranye kubindi bishunguruka bigerekeranye kubindi kugera hasi"
  76,15,Bazo cishirizwa ibikoresho vy’umwakaka hamwe n’ibikombe bibonerana
  76,16,N’ibirahuri vy’umwakaka vyujujwe kurugero rumwe rukwiye
  76,17,"Iyo\tmw’ijuru\tbazonyweshwa\tibinyobwa\tbivanzwe\tmwo\tn’ikirungo citiriwe Tangawizi"
  76,18,Urwo n’uruzi ruri mw’ijuru rwitiriwe Sal’sabila
  76,19,"Bazo kikuzwa n’imisore isharije, ubabonye womengo n’ubutare bwitiriwe Ilulu za sanzajwe"
  76,20,"Ubonye ibirimwo, uzoca ubona imigisha hamwe n’ubwami bw’Imana bunini cane"
  76,21,"Hejuru yabo barafise impuzu zihwahutse z’ibara ry’urwatsi rubisi, hamwe n’izindi zihwahutse ziremereye gatoyi, kandi bazokwambikwa ingori z’umwakaka, n’Umuremyi wabo azoba nywesha ibinyobwa vyiza cane"
  76,22,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo mpembo yanyu yibijanye n’ibikorwa vyanyu vyemewe
  76,23,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twakumanuriye iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ibice bice
  76,24,"Rero n’urindire intahe y’Umuremyi wawe, kandi ntugamburukire umwe muribo mubagira ibicumuro canke uwuhakana Imana yiwe y’ukuri"
  76,25,Ni wibuke izina ry’Umuremyi wawe mu gitondo no ku mugoroba
  76,26,"Mw’ijoro naho uyunamire ushize umutwe wawe hasi, kandi uyi ninahaze mw’ijoro mumwanya muremure"
  76,27,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taba\tbantu\tbikundira\tubuzima\tbwo\tngaha\tkw’Isi\tgusa, n’ugusiga inyuma yabo umusi ugoye cane kuribo"
  76,28,"Twebwe twabaremye n’ugushira mwo ubushobozi mubihimba vy’imibiri yabo, dushatse twoshobora kuzana abandi bantu atari bo bameze nkabo"
  76,29,"Mu vy’ukuri iki n’icibutso, rero kuwushaka azofata inzira imushikana ku Muremyi wiwe"
  76,30,"Kandi ntimushobora gushaka icarico cose Imana itabishatse, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  76,31,"Yinjiza uwo yishakiye mu migisha yayo, naba hemukiye imitima yabo yarabateguriye ibihano bibabaza cane"
  77,1,Ndarahiye kumiyaga izanwa buhoro buhoro
  77,2,No kumiyaga ihinda kunguvu nyinshi cane
  77,3,"No kumiyaga igurura ibicu, ikabigurura nkuko Imana ibishaka"
  77,4,Iga tandukanisha kure na kure ivyo bicu
  77,5,Ndarahiye kuba Marayika bashikiriza ubutumwa bw’Imana ku ntumwa z’Imana
  77,6,Mugukura impamvu kanaka canke gutuza
  77,7,Mu vy’ukuri ibi mwemerewe ntankeka bizoshika
  77,8,Mugihe inyenyeri zizo hanagurwa imico yazo
  77,9,N’amajuru igihe azo manyagurika
  77,10,N’imisozi igihe izo vungagurika
  77,11,N’intumwa z’Imana igihe zizo kwegeranywa
  77,12,Ni k’umusi uwuhe bagenewe ico gihe
  77,13,N’umusi w’intahe y’ukuri
  77,14,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musi w’intahe y’ukuri
  77,15,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,16,Mbega ntitwahoneje abantu ba kera burundu
  77,17,Hanyuma dukurikiza ko abandi bantu
  77,18,Uko niko tuzobagira abandi bazoba bari mumakosa
  77,19,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,20,Mbega ntitwabaremye mumazi ahoya hoya
  77,21,Hanyuma tuyashira ahantu haturuye
  77,22,Kugeza kukiringo kizwi
  77,23,"Natwe tugereranya umwanya w’ukuboneka kw’ikibondo, natwe ni beza mukugereranya"
  77,24,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,25,Mbega twebwe ntitwagize iy’Isi kugira ngo twegeranye abantu bose
  77,26,Mubiri bizima hamwe n’ivyapfuye
  77,27,"No\tmuriyo\tduhashira\tmwo\timisozi\tmire\tmire\titsimbataye\tneza\thasi n’ukubanywesha amazi meza y’umusarara"
  77,28,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,29,Ni mugende kuri vya bihano mwahora muhakana
  77,30,Ni mugende muri ca gitutu c’umuriro gifise impande zitatu
  77,31,"Ntikibapfuka\tico\tgitutu\tcanke\tntikibahengeshanya\tn’ukwaka\tkuwo muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  77,32,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tuwo\tmuriro\tudahera\tutanga\timishwarara\tyawo\tingana nk’amazu"
  77,33,Nkuko womengo n’ingamiya ifise ibara ry’umuhondo
  77,34,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,35,Uno musi n’umusi waho ata nakimwe bavuga
  77,36,Kandi ntibazo habwa uruhusha kugira ngo bisigure
  77,37,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,38,"Uwu\tn’umusi\tw’intahe\ty’ukuri,\ttwabegeranije\tmwese\thamwe n’ababayeho imbere yanyu"
  77,39,Ni mwaba mufise izindi ngeso ni muzigire hejuru yanje
  77,40,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,41,"Ntankeka\taba\tninahaza\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmu\tbitutu n’imyonga"
  77,42,N’ivyamwa bakunda
  77,43,"Ni mufungure kandi munywe n’akanya muneza ntangere, kubera ivyo mwahora mugira"
  77,44,Uku rero niko duhemba abagira ineza
  77,45,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,46,"Ni mufungure kandi mwinezereze gatoyi gusa, mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri abononyi"
  77,47,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,48,"Babwiwe bati :- ni mupfukame, ntibigera bapfukama namba"
  77,49,N’uruhombo kuri uwo musi ku bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  77,50,Mbega n’ibiganiro nyabaki inyuma yibi biganiro vy’amajambo y’Imana matagatifu ya Qur’ani bazo kwemera
  78,1,Babazanya inkuru nyabaki
  78,2,Ya nkuru niniya
  78,3,Ariyo batumvikana ko
  78,4,"Ni bageze ngaho, ubu vuba bazo menya ukuri kwayo"
  78,5,"Kandi ni bageze ngaho, kuko ubu vuba bazo menya ukuri kwama"
  78,6,Mbega ntitwagize iy’Isi kuba nk’ubusaswa
  78,7,N’Imisozi kuba nk’inkingi
  78,8,Turema abagabo n’abagore
  78,9,Tugira itiro ryanyu nk’Urupfu
  78,10,Tugira Ijoro nk’impuzu mwipfuka
  78,11,Tugira Umutaga nk’ukuzuka
  78,12,Twubaka hejuru yanyu Amajuru indwi akoma komeye
  78,13,Tugira itara ryaka rifise ubushuhe bukaze cane
  78,14,Dushungurura amazi ashunguruka avuye mubicu
  78,15,Kuriyo tunagishe bimwe mu bijanye n’ibiterwa
  78,16,N’imirima irimwo ibiti vyegeranye n’ibindi
  78,17,Mu vy’ukuri k’umusi w’intahe wagenewe isango ryayo ntabanduka
  78,18,Umusi hazovuzwa inzamba namwe muzorenguka muri mumirwi n’iyindi
  78,19,N’amajuru azo kwugururwa abe imiryango n’iyindi
  78,20,N’imisozi izo kurwaho ibe nk’amazi ubonera kure
  78,21,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tumuriro\twitiriwe\tJahannamu\turindiriye\tabantu\tb’inkozi z’ibibi"
  78,22,N’ubwicaro bw’abononyi
  78,23,Bazo kwicaramwo imyaka myinshi ibinjana n’ibinjana
  78,24,Ntibazo honjeramwo akabeho canke ibinyobwa
  78,25,Atari amazi abira cane hamwe n’amashira
  78,26,N’impembo ikwiranye neza n’ibikorwa vyabo
  78,27,Mu vy’ukuri ntibatinya uguharurwa n’Imana
  78,28,N’uguhakana amajambo yacu matagatifu y’Imana bimwe bihanitse
  78,29,Mugihe ibintu vyose twabifashe nka nkama mukuvyandika
  78,30,"Uno musi nimuhonje ibihano, natwe ntaco tuzobongereza atari ibihano kubindi"
  78,31,"Ntankeka\tabagamburukira\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri,\tbashiriweho\tintsinzi y’ukuri"
  78,32,Imirima hamwe n’imizabibu
  78,33,N’amasugi afise abagabo babo
  78,34,N’ibirahuri vyuzuyemwo ibinyobwa vyiza vyiza
  78,35,Ntibazo kwumva muri ayo majuru amajambo y’insaku canke amajambo y’ubuhakanyi
  78,36,Bazohembwa n’Umuremyi wawe impembo ihagije
  78,37,"Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo, nyene impuhwe nyinshi, batazoshobora kuvugana nayo"
  78,38,"Umusi imitima y’abantu bose izohagarara, hamwe n’Abamarayika bose bari kumirongo, hakaba hatazovuga kuri uwo musi atari nyene impuhwe azoba yahaye uruhusha rw’ukuvuga nawe akazo vuga amajambo y’ukuri"
  78,39,"Uwo niwo musi w’ukuri, rero uwushaka nafate inzira agende ku Muremyi wiwe"
  78,40,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turabakebuye n’ibihano biri hafi y’ugushika, umusi waho umuntu azobona ivyagizwe n’amaboko yiwe uko ari abiri, hanyuma umuhakanyi w’Imana azovuga ati:- iyo nibera ivu"
  79,1,Ndarahiye kuri ba bamarayika bakwega n’inguvu imitima y’abantu babi
  79,2,No kuri barya bakura imitima y’abantu beranda n’ubwitonzi ntangere
  79,3,No kuri barya bogana niyo mitima bayitwara ningoga na ningoga
  79,4,N’ukuyi shikana n’ingoga na n’ingoga iyo bayishikana
  79,5,N’ukuzigirira ibikenewe kuriyo
  79,6,Umusi izovuzwa inzamba yambere ikazojugumiza ibintu vyose
  79,7,Hanyuma hakurikire inzamba igira kabiri
  79,8,Kuri uwo musi imitima y’abantu izo diha diha kubera ubwoba
  79,9,Amaso yayo azoba yunamye hasi
  79,10,"Abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bazo vuga bati:- mbega ni vy’ukuri twebwe tuzosubizwa nk’uko twari tumeze aho hambere"
  79,11,Naho twoba turi amagufa masa yamaze kuribwa hagati yayo
  79,12,"Bazo\tvuga\tnkaba\ttyoza\taya\tmajambo\tbati:-\tingaruka\ty’ibi\tvyose n’uruhombo kuri twebwe"
  79,13,Mu vy’ukuri uwo musi w’imperuka uzobaho hakubiswe akaruru kamwe gusa
  79,14,Mu mwanya abantu bose bazoba bari kw’Isi nshasha
  79,15,Mbega uramaze gushikirwa n’inkuru y’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)
  79,16,"Mugihe\tUmuremyi\twiwe\tyamuhamagarira\tmu\tmwaba\tmutagatifu witiriwe Twuwa"
  79,17,"Imubwira\titi:-\tn’ugende\tkwa\tFir’auni,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tniwe\tyimonogoje n’ubwishime bwiwe"
  79,18,"Umubwire uti:- mbega wewe ugomba kwisukura"
  79,19,Nanje nzokurongora ku Muremyi wawe kugira ngo uyi gamburukire
  79,20,Rero yaramweretse ibimenyetso bikuru bikuru
  79,21,Mugabo kuri ivyo vyose yarabi hakanye ariyonkora
  79,22,Mu nyuma yarasubiye inyuma atangura kwihangana kugira ngo azitire abantu ntibakurikire intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)
  79,23,Yarakoranije abantu abahamagara
  79,24,"Avuga ati :- ni jewe Muremyi wanyu mukuru"
  79,25,Aho niho Imana yamufata mukuboko kwiwe mukuriha kumvugo yiwe ya nyuma hamwe n’imvugo yiwe yambere
  79,26,Mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo utuzwa kuri bamwe batinya Imana yabo y’ukuri
  79,27,"Mbega ni mwebwe mufise iremwa rikomeye gusumba, canke Amajuru ? Niyo yayubatse"
  79,28,Irerura ayo Majuru kubungane bwayo n’ukuzigira neza
  79,29,"N’ugushiramwo umwijima w’Ijoro ryawo, n’uguserura Umutaga wayo"
  79,30,Munyuma yaho Isi arayisasa
  79,31,"Ayikuramwo amazi yayo, hamwe n’amarisho yayo"
  79,32,N’Imisozi yose arayi hagarika
  79,33,Kugira ngo ibanezereze mwebwe bantu hamwe n’ibikoko vyanyu vyose
  79,34,Mugihe hazoshika uwo musi uhambaye
  79,35,Umusi umuntu azokwibuka ivyo yagize vyose
  79,36,"N’umuriro\tukaze\tcane\tuzo\tkwerekanwa\tk’umuntu\tuwariwe\twese awubona"
  79,37,Nayo wamwononyi
  79,38,Yakunda cane ubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi
  79,39,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tumuriro\tudahera\twitiriwe\tJahannamu\tniho\thazoba\thari ubwicaro bwiwe"
  79,40,Nayo umwe yatinya guhagarikwa imbere y’Umuremyi wiwe n’ukubuza umutima wiwe n’amatamariro y’ibintu bibi
  79,41,Rero mw’Ijuru niho hazoba ubwicaro bwiwe
  79,42,Barakubaza umusi w’umuhero w’Isi n’ukuboneka kwawo kuzoba ryari
  79,43,Kuri hehe kugira ngo dushobore kuwuvuga
  79,44,Inyuma y’ubumenyi bwayo bwose buri ku Muremyi wawe
  79,45,Wewe uri mubatuza abantu gusa k’uwutinya uwo musi w’imperuka
  79,46,Umusi bazowubona bazoba nk’abaticaye ng’aha kw’Isi atari umugoroba umwe wonyene gusa canke umutaga wawo gusa
  80,1,Yarazinze mumaso yiwe n’uguhindukiza amaso yiwe
  80,2,Kubera yuko yashikiwe n’impumyi
  80,3,None n’igiki cakumenyesheje nkumbure azo kwisukura
  80,4,Canke azo kwibuka ico cibutso gishobore kumufasha
  80,5,Nayo uwuzo bona yuko ataco akeneye mw’idini arimwo
  80,6,Ari wewe umwitaho gusumba
  80,7,Kandi sikuri wewe natasukuka
  80,8,Mugabo uwukwituye
  80,9,Nawe atinya
  80,10,Na wewe nt’umwiteho
  80,11,"Oya sivyo, mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’ani n’impanuro"
  80,12,Kuwukunda uwariwe wese azonyurwa
  80,13,Kumpapuro z’iteka
  80,14,Zatewe iteka kandi zisukuwe
  80,15,Ziri muminwe y’abanditsi b’Imana
  80,16,Bafise iteka kandi baninahaza Imana yabo y’ukuri
  80,17,Umuntu yaratakaye mukubandanya n’ubuhakanyi bwiwe
  80,18,Niku kintu nyabaki yamuremye mwo
  80,19,"Kw’ima\try’intanga\tniryo\tyamuremye\tmwo\tn’ukumuha\tububasha bukwiye"
  80,20,Hanyuma imworohereza inzira yoroshe
  80,21,Hanyuma iramwica nukumushira mu ntatemwa yiwe
  80,22,Hanyuma mugihe izoshakira izo muzura
  80,23,Oya! ntaraheza ivyo yamutegetse Umuremyi wiwe
  80,24,Umuntu niyitegereze ibifungurwa vyiwe
  80,25,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twasukiye amazi kunguvu tuyakuye mubicu
  80,26,N’ukumanyagura Isi ibimanyu manyu
  80,27,Muriyo tunagisha ibifungurwa bitandukanye vy’intete
  80,28,N’imizabibu hamwe n’ivyakatsi biribwa
  80,29,N’imizayituni hamwe n’imitende
  80,30,N’imirima irimwo ibiti vyegeranyeko n’ibindi
  80,31,N’ivyamwa hamwe n’ivyatsi vy’ibitungwa
  80,32,Mukuba nezereza mwebwe bantu hamwe n’ibikoko vyanyu
  80,33,Mugihe hazoshika ijwi rikaze cane ribabaza amatwi
  80,34,N’umusi waho umuntu azohunga mwene wabo
  80,35,Na nyina wiwe hamwe na Se wiwe
  80,36,N’umutambukanyi wiwe hamwe n’ibibondo vyiwe
  80,37,Umuntu wese muribo kuri uwo musi azoba afise ibimuhagije wenyene
  80,38,Kuri uwo musi ayandi maso y’abantu azoba asayangana
  80,39,Azo twenga asusurutse neza
  80,40,"N’ayandi maso kuri uwo musi, azoba afise inkungugu kuriyo"
  80,41,Umwijima ukaze cane uzoba ubapfutse
  80,42,Abo nibo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri b’inkozi z’ibibi
  81,1,Igihe izuba rizo zingwa zingwa
  81,2,N’Inyenyeri nazo mugihe zizo hunguruka
  81,3,N’Imisozi nayo mugihe izo gendeshwa
  81,4,N’Ingamiya ziri mumezi yazo mugihe zizo tabwa
  81,5,N’Ibikoko vyo mw’ishamba mugihe bizo kwegeranywa
  81,6,N’ibiyaga navyo mugihe bizoturirwa
  81,7,N’Imitima y’abantu nayo mugihe izoteranywa n’imibiri yavyo
  81,8,N’umwana w’umwigeme yahambwe akiri muzima mugihe azo bazwa
  81,9,Kucaha nyabaki yatumwe agandagurwa
  81,10,N’ibitabu vy’ibikorwa vy’abantu mugihe bizokwizwa ku bantu bose
  81,11,N’ifukisho ry’Ijuru mugihe rizo fukurwa
  81,12,N’Umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu mugihe uzo huherwa
  81,13,N’Ijuru igihe rizo kwegerezwa
  81,14,Umutima w’umumwe wese uzo menya ico washikirije
  81,15,Rero ndarahiye kunyenyeri zisubira inyuma
  81,16,Zigenda hanyuma zika zimangana
  81,17,No kw’Ijoro mugihe ryinjiye
  81,18,No mugitondo mugihe hakeye
  81,19,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tiyi\tQur’ani\tntagatifu\tn’amajambo\tyazananye\tn’intumwa y’Imana ntagatifu Jibrilu (iii)"
  81,20,Afise inguvu n’icubahiro c’iteka imbere y’Imana
  81,21,Agamburukirwa iyo mw’Ijuru hanyuma akaba yizigirwa
  81,22,Yuko mugenzi wanyu atari umusazi
  81,23,"Mu vy’ukuri yaramubonye Umumarayika Jibrilu (iii) kurugero\trw’amaso ruboneka neza"
  81,24,Kandi s’ingumyi w’ibintu bitazwi
  81,25,Kandi aya s’amajambo ya Shetani yirukanywe mumigisha y’Imana
  81,26,None muja hehe
  81,27,Ntiyari kuba iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu atari uko ari icibutso ku bantu bose
  81,28,Uwushaka muri mwebwe gufata inzira igororotse
  81,29,Namwe ntimuzo kwemera atari uko Imana Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose yabishatse
  82,1,Igihe amajuru azo satagurika
  82,2,N’inyenyeri igihe zizo hunguruka
  82,3,N’ibiyaga igihe bizo saturwa
  82,4,N’intatemwa z’abantu igihe zizo zurwa
  82,5,"Umutima\tw’umuntu\tuzomenya\tico\twatanguje\tkugira\thamwe\tn’ico wasigaje inyuma"
  82,6,Wewe muntu! ni igiki kiguhenda n’Umuremyi wawe mutagatifu
  82,7,"Uwakuremye nuku kugira neza, hanyuma nuku kuringaniza neza"
  82,8,Mw’ishusho iryariryo ryose yishakiye niko yakuringanije
  82,9,"None si uko, ahubwo mwebwe nimwe muhakana uwo musi w’impembo"
  82,10,Mu vy’ukuri hejuru yanyu hari abantu babashigikiye
  82,11,Bafise iteka kandi bandika
  82,12,Bafise ubumenyi bwivyo mugira vyose
  82,13,Mu vy’ukuri abagira ineza bose bazoba bari mumahirwe
  82,14,N’abagizi b’inabi bose bazoba bari mu muriro udahera
  82,15,Bazo kwinjira muriwo k’umusi w’impembo
  82,16,Kandi ntibazowuva mwo
  82,17,N’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musi w’impembo yuko uzoba ari umusi wa ryari
  82,18,Kandi n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musi w’impembo y’uko uzoba ari umusi wa ryari
  82,19,"N’umusi waho umutima w’umuntu utazo shigikira umutima w’uwundi muntu kukintu icarico cose, n’itegeko ryuwo musi rizoba ari iry’Imana gusa"
  83,1,Uguhonywa kw’abantu kuzoba shikira kuba zimba abandi
  83,2,Mugihe bipimiye ku bantu bakira ibipimo bikwiye
  83,3,"Mugabo bapimiye abantu kumagemeri canke kuminzani baca\tbagabanya ko"
  83,4,Mbega ntibiyumvira yuko bazo zurwa
  83,5,K’umusi uzoba ari umusi mukuru
  83,6,"K’umusi\tabantu\tbose\tbazohagarara\timbere\ty’Umuremyi\tw’ibiremwa vyose"
  83,7,"None sivyo, mu vy’ukuri inyandiko z’abantu babi ziri mu gitabu citiriwe Sijjini"
  83,8,"None n’ijambo nyabaki rizo kumenyesha ico gitabu citiriwe Sijjini\ty’uko ari ikintu nyabaki"
  83,9,N’igitabu canditswe mwo ibikorwa vy’abantu babi
  83,10,Kuri uwo musi ibihano bikaze cane bizoshikira ku bantu bahakana
  83,11,Abahakana umusi w’impembo
  83,12,"Kandi\tntawuhakana\tatari\tuwarenze\timbibe\tzagenywe\tn’Imana,\tkandi bafise ibicumuro"
  83,13,"Asomewe\tamajambo\tyacu\tmatagatifu\taca\tavuga\tati:-\tizo\tn’ingeso z’abantu baho hambere"
  83,14,None sivyo ! Ahubwo bashize ku mitima yabo ingutu kumabi bahora bagira
  83,15,None si uko ! mu vy’ukuri bazo hagarikwa kuri uwo musi w’imperuka n’Umuremyi wabo
  83,16,Hanyuma bazokwinjira mu muriro udahera
  83,17,"Hanyuma babwirwe bati :- ibi nivyo mwahora muhakana"
  83,18,"None\tsivyo !\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tinzandiko\tz’abantu\tberanda\tziri\tmugitabu citiriwe Iliyyiin"
  83,19,None n’ijambo nyabaki rizo kumenyesha kugira ngo umenye iyo Iliyyin yuko ari ikintu nyabaki
  83,20,N’igitabu canditswe mwo ibikorwa vy’abantu beranda
  83,21,Ababibona ni barya batumire batumiwe n’Imana
  83,22,Mu vy’ukuri abagira ineza bazoba bari mu migisha myiza ntangere
  83,23,Bicare kunyegamo z’iteka barabana
  83,24,Uzobona ibimenyetso vy’imigisha ku maso yabo
  83,25,Bazo nyweshwa ibinyobwa vyugawe n’imipfundikizo myiza
  83,26,"Mu nyuma yivyo ivyo binyobwa nivyo bizana akamoto kitiriwe Miski, mugabo mu kuronka ibi vyose nibahiganwe abahiganwa bose"
  83,27,N’ivangwa ryiyo Miski rivanzwe n’amazi yitiriwe Tasniim
  83,28,Naryo n’isoko bazonywera mwo abantu begeranywe n’Imana
  83,29,Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahora bagira ibicumuro bahora batwenga abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  83,30,"Baciye hambavu yabo, baca bakubitana ingohe babacokora"
  83,31,"Bagarutse ku bantu babo, bagaruka bafise akamwemwe ntangere"
  83,32,"Baba bonye baca bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri abo bantu nibo bazimiye aribo ba Isilamu"
  83,33,Nayo abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri ntibarungitswe kuba Isilamu kugira ngo baba cungere
  83,34,"Uno musi abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri, bazo batwenga aba hakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  83,35,Bazoba bari hejuru y’inyegamo z’iteka barabana kumigisha yabo
  83,36,"Mbega abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, barahawe impembo yivyo bahora bagira"
  84,1,Igihe Amajuru azo satagurika
  84,2,Nigihe azo tega amatwi arekuriwe n’Umuremyi wayo
  84,3,N’Isi nayo mugihe izo sanzazwa
  84,4,N’ugukura ivyari muriyo igasigara igaragara
  84,5,Igatega amatwi ku Muremyi wayo n’ukwemererwa
  84,6,"Wa muntu we ! mu vy’ukuri wewe urita kurutare kugeza aho muzohura n’Umuremyi wawe, rero ivyo bikorwa vyawe uzobisanga iwe"
  84,7,Nayo uwuzo habwa igitabu ciwe m’ukuboko kwiwe kw’iburyo
  84,8,Rero uyo muntu azo harurwa n’ibiharuro vyoroshe cane
  84,9,"Kandi\tazosubira\tku\tbantu\tbiwe\tmugihe\tazoba\tafise\takanya\tkuneza ntangere"
  84,10,Mugabo uwuzo habwa igitabu ciwe imugongo
  84,11,Uyo muntu azo saba urupfu
  84,12,Kandi azo kwinjira mu muriro udahera
  84,13,Kuko yari afise akanya muneza hamwe n’abiwe
  84,14,Yiketse yuko atazo garuka ku Mana yiwe
  84,15,N’ukubera iki atagarukira Umuremyi wiwe yamye amubona
  84,16,Rero ndarahiye k’ugutukura kw’izuba bugorovye
  84,17,No kw’Ijoro hamwe nivyo ryegeranye
  84,18,No k’Ukwezi mugihe gukwijije imisi yakwo
  84,19,Muzo hura n’ivyabaye hamwe n’ibindi
  84,20,None bafise iki ko batemera
  84,21,Mugihe basomewe iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ntibayi gamburukira
  84,22,Mugabo bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baguma bahakana gusa
  84,23,N’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bwivyo begeranya
  84,24,Rero n’ubabwire ibihano bibabaza cane
  84,25,"Dukuyemwo abemeye Imana bimwe bivuye k’umitima yabo n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza, abo nibo bazoba bafise impembo idahera"
  85,1,Ndarahiye ku Majuru afise Inyenyeri
  85,2,No k’umusi w’isango bemerewe
  85,3,N’uwuzoba icabona kuki boneshwa
  85,4,"Barahonejwe\tabantu\tbatoteje\taba\tIsilamu\rbari\tkubirindiro\tvyabo\rvyo\rmubinogo"
  85,5,Bifise umuriro w’inkwi nyinshi cane
  85,6,Mugihe bari bicaye ngaho
  85,7,Nabo bitegereza ivyo bagirirwa abo ba Isilamu
  85,8,"Nabo batara bona inabi iyariyo yose kuri bo, atari ukwemera Imana yabo ariyo nyene intsinzi n’uguhayagizwa bimwe bikwiye"
  85,9,"Ikaba ariyo nyene ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi, n’Imana niyo ibona ibintu vyose"
  85,10,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batoteza aba Isilamu b’abagabo hamwe naba Isilamu kazi, hanyuma ntibasabe imbabazi, abo bantu bazoronka ibihano vyo mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, kandi bazoronka ibihano biba turira neza cane"
  85,11,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri, nukugira ibikorwa vyiza ntankeka bazoronka imirima irimwo inzuzi zica imbere yabo, iyi niyo ntsinzi niniya"
  85,12,Mu vy’ukuri uguhana kw’Umuremyi wawe kurakaze cane
  85,13,Niyo yatanguje kurema ibiremwa vyose naniyo izobagarura
  85,14,"Nayo niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi, n’ugukunda ibiremwa vyayo vyose"
  85,15,Nyene inyegamo y’iteka ntagatifu
  85,16,Umugizi w’ukugira ico yishakiye cose
  85,17,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru z’ingabo z’abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  85,18,Ariwe Fir’auni hamwe na Thamudu
  85,19,Mugabo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bagumye badadaza gusa
  85,20,N’Imana iraba kikuje kumpande zose
  85,21,Ahubwo iyi ni Qur’ani ntagatifu
  85,22,Kuri urwo rubaho rushinguwe neza
  86,1,Ndarahiye ku Majuru hamwe n’icoza mw’Ijoro
  86,2,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha ico kintu kizoza mw’Ijoro
  86,3,N’Inyenyeri yaka cane
  86,4,Nta mutima w’Umuntu uwariwe wese atari uko ufise uwuwu cungereye hejuru yiwe
  86,5,"Ahubwo umuntu niyirabe neza, yaremwe mu kintu nyabaki"
  86,6,Yaremwe mumazi asunitswe
  86,7,Avuye hagati y’amagufa y’umugongo n’igikiriza
  86,8,Mu vy’ukuri Imana irafise ubushobozi bw’ukumugarura
  86,9,Umusi hazoserurwa amabanga y’abantu bose
  86,10,Rero nta bushobozi azoba afise canke umufasha
  86,11,Ndarahiye kubicu bizana imvura
  86,12,No kw’Isi isaduka ikazana ibiterwa
  86,13,"Yuko iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, n’imvugo itandukanya ukuri kwama"
  86,14,Kandi si ibijajuro
  86,15,Mu vy’ukuri n’abagira ingeso kuzindi
  86,16,Nanje izo ngeso zabo ndazitereye kure
  86,17,"Nubahe abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, umwanya mutoyi gusa"
  87,1,Ninahaza izina ry’Umuremyi wawe mutagatifu
  87,2,Uwaremye ibintu vyose nukubi ringaniza
  87,3,"Nukugerageza kimwe kukindi, nukukirongora"
  87,4,Niya nagishije ivyakatsi vyose
  87,5,Hanyuma nukuyigira ivyumye n’ibara ryirabura
  87,6,Tuzo kwigisha kandi ntuzo kwibagira
  87,7,Mugabo Imana ibishatse niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiboneka hamwe nibita boneka
  87,8,Natwe tuzo kworohereza idini ryoroshe
  87,9,Rero nubashikirize ubwo butumwa nibwaba bushoboka
  87,10,Ntankeka azokwibuka uwutinya Imana yiwe y’ukuri
  87,11,Uwufise ibihano vyinshi azoba kure y’ubwo butumwa
  87,12,Uwuzo kwinjira mu muriro udahera muniniya cane
  87,13,Hanyuma muri uwo muriro udahera ntazopfa canke ntazoba muzima
  87,14,Mu vy’ukuri aramaze kuronka intsinzi uwisukuye n’amabi
  87,15,Akibuka izina ry’Umuremyi wiwe n’ugusenga
  87,16,Mugabo mwebwe mukunda cane ubuzima bwo ngaha kw’Isi
  87,17,Mugihe ubuzima bwo mw’ijuru aribwo bwiza gusumba kandi buramba
  87,18,"Mu vy’ukuri ibi vyose, biri mu bitabu vy’akahise. hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana"
  87,19,Ibitabu vy’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)
  88,1,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru y’ivyago bizopfuka ibiremwa vyose
  88,2,Uwo musi amaso y’abantu azoba afise ibimaramare vyinshi cane
  88,3,N’ukugira imirimo ikoma komeye cane iruhisha
  88,4,Binjire mu muriro udahera waka cane
  88,5,Bazonyweshwa muri ayo mariba abira ukuri kwama
  88,6,Ntabifungurwa bazoba bafise atari ibifungurwa vy’amahwa gusa
  88,7,Ntibivyibuhisha canke ngo bikure ikigoyi
  88,8,Amaso y’abandi bantu kuri uwo musi w’imperuka azoba asayangana neza
  88,9,Azoba yashimiwe kubera ibikorwa vyabo bagize
  88,10,Zizoba ziri mw’ijuru ry’iteka ntangere
  88,11,Ntizizo kwumva muri ayo majuru ibidafise akamaro
  88,12,Harimwo amariba y’amazi ashunguruka neza
  88,13,Harimwo n’inyegamo z’iteka zitaramuwe hejuru
  88,14,N’ibirahuri bishinguwe neza
  88,15,N’imisego itondeshejwe kumirongo n’iyindi
  88,16,N’ibirago bishashwe neza biteye igomwe
  88,17,Mbega ntibitegereza igene Ingamiya yaremwe
  88,18,N’Amajuru ingene yareruwe
  88,19,N’Imisozi igene yatsimbatajwe
  88,20,N’Isi igene twayaguye
  88,21,Rero niwibutse mu vy’ukuri wewe n’uwibutsa abantu gusa
  88,22,Wewe suwo kubaca imvutu
  88,23,Mugabo uwusubiye inyuma n’uguhakana Umuremyi wiwe w’ukuri
  88,24,Imana izo muhana ibihano bininiya cane
  88,25,Mu vy’ukuri ingaruka yabo niyizoba iwacu
  88,26,Hanyuma ntankeka iharurwa ryabo riri hejuru yacu
  89,1,Ndarahiye k’Umutwenzi
  89,2,No kumisi icumi
  89,3,"No ku bintu bibiri bibiri, canke kuri kimwe kimwe"
  89,4,No kw’Ijiro rirenganye
  89,5,"Hari muri ibi, indahiro k’uwufise ubwenge agatinya"
  89,6,Mbega ntiwabonye ingene Umuremyi wawe yagiriye bene Aadi
  89,7,Abo bene Irama bari bafise amazu mare mare
  89,8,Abo bantu bataremwe nk’abandi bantu mubindi bisagara
  89,9,Na Thamuda aribo babaje imisozi kumbuga zabo
  89,10,Na Fir’auni nyene amazu nk’inkingi zikiriho n’ubu
  89,11,Abagize amabi mubisagara
  89,12,Hanyuma bararengeje urugero muri ivyo bisagara kumabi atako avurwa
  89,13,Kuri ivyo Umuremyi wawe yarabakubise inkoni imwe gusa y’ibihano
  89,14,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe ari mw’iperereza
  89,15,"Mugabo umuntu Umuremyi wiwe yamuhaye ibibazo n’ukumuha iteka n’ukumuha imigisha nawe agaca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje wampaye iteka ntangere"
  89,16,"Nigihe imuhaye ibibazo nukumu gabaniriza imigisha yiwe, aca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje uramaramaje"
  89,17,"Suko, ahubwo mwebwe ntimuraba impfuvyi n’ijsho ry’ikigongwe"
  89,18,Kandi mwebwe ntimwihimiriza kurisha abakene
  89,19,Kandi murarya ibisigi vy’abantu n’igihababu cinshi cane
  89,20,Kandi murakunda amatungo k’urugero rurengeje ibintu vyose
  89,21,"Suko bimeze, mugihe Isi izo manyagurwa ibimanyu manyu"
  89,22,N’Umuremyi wanyu azoshika ari kumwe n’Abamarayika bari kumirongo n’iyindi
  89,23,"Rero kuri uwo musi hazo shikirizwa wa muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, kuri uwo musi umuntu azokwibuka, mugabo uko kwibuka kwiwe kuzo mumarira iki"
  89,24,"Azovuga ati:- iyo ntanguza ineza kubera ubuzima bwanje"
  89,25,Rero uwo musi Imana ntizohana umuntu uwariwe wese nkuko Imana ihora ihana
  89,26,Kandi ntizo boha uwariwe wese nkuko ihora ibaboha
  89,27,Ewe mutima uhumuye
  89,28,"N’ugaruke ku Muremyi wawe\twizeye yuko utekaniwe, n’Imana\tnayo itekanirwe na wewe"
  89,29,Rero niwinjire mumirwi y’abantu beranda
  89,30,Winjire mw’Ijuru ryanje
  90,1,Ndarahiye kuri iki gisagara c’Imakkat
  90,2,Na wewe uzomanuka muri iki gisagara nyene
  90,3,"Ndarahiye kukintu cavyaye, hamwe nicavutse"
  90,4,Yuko twaremye ikiremwa muntu mungorane nyinshi cane
  90,5,Mbega yiyumvira yuko ata n’umwe yoshobora kumufata
  90,6,"Avuga ati:- narononye amatungo menshi cane"
  90,7,Mbega yiyumvira yuko ata n’umwe amubona
  90,8,Mbega ntitwamuhaye amaso abiri
  90,9,N’ururimi hamwe n’iminwa ibiri
  90,10,Tumwereka inzira zose uko ari zibiri
  90,11,Mbega yarawusatuye uwo musozi
  90,12,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha uwo musozi
  90,13,N’uguha umushumvyi uburenganzira bwiwe n’iteka rimukwiye
  90,14,Canke ukamurisha k’umusi w’ikigoyi
  90,15,Impfuvyi y’umugenzi n’iyitari iyumugenzi
  90,16,Canke umukene ataco yifashije
  90,17,"Hanyuma\tabe\tmubemeye\tImana\tyiwe\ty’ukuri,\tnukuburirana ukwihangana nukuburirana mukugiriranira ikigongwe"
  90,18,Abo nibo bantu bo kuruhande rw’amahoro
  90,19,"Mugabo abahakanye amajambo yacu matagatifu, abo nibo bantu bo kuruhande rw’ishari"
  90,20,Umuriro wugarijwe kumpande zose uzoba uri hejuru yabo
  91,1,Ndarahiye kw’Izuba no kumishwarara yaryo
  91,2,No k’Ukwezi kugu kurikira
  91,3,No k’Umutaga uku boneshereza
  91,4,No kw’Ijoro mugihe kuripfuse
  91,5,No ku Majuru hamwe n’uwayubatse
  91,6,No kw’Isi hamwe n’uwayishashe
  91,7,No k’umutima hamwe n’uwawuringanije
  91,8,Hanyuma arawubwira amabi y’awo n’ivyiza vyawo
  91,9,Ntankeka arafise intsinzi uwasukuye umutima wiwe
  91,10,Kandi ntankeka yarahomvye uwa cinyije umutima wiwe
  91,11,Ba Thamuda barahakanye Umuremyi wabo kubera ukuzimira kwabo
  91,12,Mugihe yahagarara umwe mubabisha babo mukuru
  91,13,"Aho niho intumwa y’Imana yababwira iti:- iyi n’Ingamiya y’Imana ni muyireke hamwe n’ibinyobwa vyayo"
  91,14,"Mugabo barayihakanye iyo ntumwa y’Imana barayica, kuri ivyo rero Umuremyi wabo aca arabahonya kubera ibicumuro vyabo nukuba hanagura burundu"
  91,15,Kandi ntibatinya ingaruka yavyo
  92,1,Ndarahiye kw’Ijoro ripfuka ibintu vyose
  92,2,No k’Umutaga utanga umuco wayo
  92,3,No kuwaremye ikigabo n’ikigore
  92,4,Yuko ibikorwa vyanyu bitandukanye
  92,5,Umwe atanga nugutinya Imana yiwe
  92,6,N’ukwemera ijambo ryiza
  92,7,Tuzo mworohereza inzira yukuja mw’ijuru
  92,8,N’uwigira ingumyi ntiyiteho kubindi biremwa nkawe
  92,9,N’uguhakana ibintu vyiza
  92,10,Tuzo mworohereza inzira y’ukuja muriro udahera
  92,11,N’amatungo yiwe ntaco azomumarira mugihe azoba ariko aranyikira mu muriro udahera
  92,12,Mu vy’ukuri nikuri twebwe kuba menyesha ibiremwa vyose inzira nziza hamwe n’inzira y’ishari
  92,13,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turafise Ijuru n’Isi
  92,14,Rero nimugabe n’umuriro udahera waka n’inguvu nyinshi cane
  92,15,Ntawuzo winjira mwo atari umuntu mubi
  92,16,Ariwe ahakana n’ukuyiha umugongo iyi dini y’ukuri
  92,17,"Nuwu\tgamburukira\tImana\tyiwe\ty’ukuri\tazokingirwa\tnuwo\tmuriro udahera"
  92,18,Uwutanga amatungo yiwe kugira ngo yisukure
  92,19,Mugihe ata n’umwe yamugiriye ineza kugira ngo abe aramuriha iyo neza
  92,20,Atari ukurondera impuhwe z’Umuremyi wiwe mutagatifu
  92,21,Rero azoronka ikizo muhumuriza
  93,1,Ndarahiye k’Umutaga
  93,2,No kw’Ijoro riba rikwiragiye hose
  93,3,"Ntiyagusize Umuremyi wawe, canke ntiyashavuye"
  93,4,Ntankeka mugihe kiza kizoba ari ciza kuri wewe gusumba icabaye
  93,5,N’Umuremyi wawe azoguha vyinshi kugeza aho uzoshima
  93,6,Mbega nti yagusanze uri impfuvyi ica iguha uburaro n’uburamuko bwiza
  93,7,Igusanga utazi kurongora inzira nayo irakurongora
  93,8,Igusanga uri umukene iguha n’ubutunzi
  93,9,Rero ntubonere impfuvyi
  93,10,Kandi ntukankamire uwukubajije
  93,11,N’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe uyivuge
  94,1,Mbega ntitwakwaguriye igikiriza cawe
  94,2,Nukugukurira uburemere bwawe wari ufise
  94,3,Bwavunye umugongo wawe
  94,4,Nukuguhayagiza kukuvurwa kwawe
  94,5,"Rero mu vy’ukuri hamwe n’ingorane, haraboneka agahengwe"
  94,6,"Mu vy’ukuri hamwe n’ingorane, haraboneka agahengwe"
  94,7,"Niwaheza\tgushikiriza\tubutumwa\tbwawe,\tn’ubandaye\tn’amasengesho yawe"
  94,8,Kandi wiyegereze cane ku Muremyi wawe
  95,1,Ndarahiye kuri iki camwa citiriweTtiyn na Zaytuni
  95,2,No k’umusozi wa Sinayi
  95,3,No kuri iki gisagara c’amahoro c’IMakkat
  95,4,Ntankeka twaremye umuntu mw’ishusho ryiza cane
  95,5,Hanyuma tumugarura kuba hasi gusumba abari hasi cane
  95,6,"Dukuyemwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza,\tabo nibo bazoronka impembo itazo hera"
  95,7,N’igiki kigushikira n’uguhakana impembo munyuma y’ukubona ivyo vyose
  95,8,Ntabwo Allah arenganura abacamanza
  96,1,N’usome kw’izina ry’Umuremyi wawe yaremye
  96,2,Yaremye umuntu kukimanyu c’amaraso
  96,3,"N’usome, n’Umuremyi wawe n’umugira neza cane"
  96,4,Niyo yigishije umuntu ikoresheje ikaramu
  96,5,Yigishije umuntu ibintu atari abifitiye ubumenyi
  96,6,"None s’ibi, mu vy’ukuri umuntu yama yishima"
  96,7,Akishima yuko yaronse ubutunzi
  96,8,Ntankeka ingaruka ya bose iri ku Muremyi wawe gusa
  96,9,Mbega wabonye umwe amubuza
  96,10,Umuntu mweranda ariko arasenga
  96,11,Mbega wabonye yuko ari hejuru y’uburongozi
  96,12,Canke ategeka kugira ibikorwa vyiza
  96,13,Mbega ubona gute ko yoba ari umuhakanyi w’Imana y’ukuri nugusubira inyuma
  96,14,Mbega ntabumenyi afise yuko Imana imubona
  96,15,"None s’ibi, nata reka kugira ivyo agira, twebwe tuzomukwega kumishatsi yiwe yo kuga hori hori k’umutwe wiwe"
  96,16,Aga hori hori k’umubeshi gafise ibicumuro
  96,17,N’ahamagare basoma mbike biwe bamufashe
  96,18,Natwe tuzohamagara aba Marayika bo mu muriro udahera bamuhane
  96,19,"None\ts’ibi,\tntumugamburukire,\tahubwo\tn’upfukame\tushire\tumutwe wawe hasi ube hafi cane y’Umuremyi wawe"
  97,1,Mu vy’ukuri twamanuye iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu mw’Ijoro ry’iteka ryitiriwe Laylatul’Qadri
  97,2,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha yuko ariryo joro ritagatifu ry’iteka ryitiriwe Laylatul’Qadri
  97,3,Iryo joro ry’iteka ntangere niryo ryiza gusumba amezi igihumbi
  97,4,"Hamanuka Abamarayika bafise imitima y’ibiremwa vyeranda, muri iryo joro kw’itegeko ry’Umuremyi wabo kubintu vyose"
  97,5,N’amahoro yiryo joro kugeza kw’iseruko ry’umutwenzi
  98,1,"Bamwe\tbahakanye\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tmu\tbantu\tbahawe\tigitabu gitagatifu, hamwe nabagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, ntibazoreka kugira ivyo basanganywe bagira, kugeza aho bazoshikirwa n’ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro"
  98,2,Intumwa yavuye ku Mana ibasomera impapuro zisukuye
  98,3,Muri izo harimwo amategeko akoma komeye
  98,4,Kandi abo bantu ntibacanyemwo mubahawe igitabu c’Imana gitagatifu atari uko munyuma bashikiwe n’ivyemezo bashaka
  98,5,"Kandi ntibategetswe kugira icarico cose atari ugusenga Imana yonyene gusa, mugusukura idini ryiwe, n’ukureka gusenga amadini y’ubuzimire, hanyuma bace bahagarika amasengesho n’ugutanga imperezwa, iyo rero niyo dini ihagaze neza y’ukuri"
  98,6,"Ntankeka bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri mu bantu bahawe igitabu c’Imana c’ukuri, hamwe n’abagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, bazo kwinjira mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu bawicare mwo mu buzima bwabo bwose, kuko abo nibo biremwa bibi cane"
  98,7,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza, abo nibo bantu beranda mubiremwa vy’Imana"
  98,8,"Impembo yabo iri ku Muremyi wabo, n’imirima y’ubuzima bwabo bwose budahera, kuko muriyo haca imbere yabo imyonga, baze babeyo mu buzima bwabo bwose, kuko Imana yarabemereye nabo barashima, iyo mpembo ni kuri urya muntu atinya Umuremyi wiwe"
  99,1,Mugihe Isi izo nyiganzwa inyigangizo rininiya cane
  99,2,N’igihe izosohora ibiyiremereye kuriyo vyose
  99,3,"N’umuntu yaravuze ati:- mbega uno musi kuri iy’Isi hari iki"
  99,4,Kuri uwo musi Isi izo sesangura inkuru zayo zose
  99,5,Kuko Umuremyi wayo yayitegetse kugira gutyo
  99,6,"Kuri uwo musi abantu bazova muntatemwa zabo bari imigwi n’iyindi, kugira ngo berekwe ibikorwa vyabo bagize"
  99,7,"Rero\tuwagize\tivyiza\tnaho\tvyoba\tbingana\tn’uburemere\tbw’akanyegeri azobona impembo yavyo"
  99,8,N’uwagize amabi naho yoba angana n’uburemere bw’akanyegeri azobona impembo yavyo
  100,1,Ndarahiye kw’Ifarasi zigenda cane kandi zihema hema
  100,2,Zigasohora umucanwa kumaguru yazo mugukubita amaguru yazo hasi
  100,3,Zigatera mugihe co mu gitondo
  100,4,Zigatumura inkungugu nyinshi muri ico gihe nyene
  100,5,Zikinjira mumirwi y’abansi kurwana
  100,6,Ntankeka umuntu arahakana Umuremyi wiwe
  100,7,Nawe azi ibi vyose
  100,8,Akaba afise urukundo runiniya cane rw’ugukunda amatungo
  100,9,Mbega ntazi yuko igihe bazozurwa abari muntatemwa zabo
  100,10,Mugihe hazoserurwa ibiri mubikiriza vyabo
  100,11,Yuko Umuremyi wabo azobamenya neza cane kuri uwo musi ibiremwa vyiwe vyose
  101,1,Ivyago bikubita kumitima y’abantu ariwo muhero w’Isi
  101,2,Ivyo vyago bikubita kumutima y’abantu n’ibihe
  101,3,N’ijambo nyabaki rizo kumenyesha yuko ivyo vyago bikubita kumitima y’abantu nivyahe
  101,4,N’umusi waho abantu bazoba nk’abana b’inzige bashwabagiye hose
  101,5,N’imisozi izoba nk’isufi zasanzajwe zitumukira hejuru
  101,6,Rero uwo k’umunzani wiwe uzoba uremereye
  101,7,Uyo muntu azoba ari mubuzima bumubereye
  101,8,Uwuzoba afise k’umunzani wiwe uhoya hoya
  101,9,"Uyo muntu ubwicaro bwiwe buzoba ari ubwo mumuriro\tudahera witiriwe Hawiyat"
  101,10,None n’ijambo nyabaki rizo kumenyesha uwo muriro witiriwe Hawiyat
  101,11,N’umucanwa waka cane
  102,1,"Mwasamaye\tmukurondera\tubwinshi\tbw’amatungo\tmenshi\tn’ibibondo hamwe n’ukwihayagiza kurivyo"
  102,2,Kugeza aho mugendera intatemwa z’abantu
  102,3,Suko! Ubu vuba muzo menya yuko atarivyo
  102,4,Kandi suko! Ubu vuba muzo menya yuko atarivyo
  102,5,Suko! Iyo mwoba mufise ubumenyi bw’ukuri
  102,6,Mu vy’ukuri muzobona umuriro udahera
  102,7,"Hanyuma, mu vy’ukuri muzo wubona uwo muriro bimwe vy’ukuri"
  102,8,"Hanyuma, mu vy’ukuri muzo bazwa kuri uwo musi kubijanye n’imigisha mwahawe, n’ingene mwayikoresheje"
  103,1,Ndarahiye k’umwanya w’umuhingamo
  103,2,Yuko umuntu ari m’uruhombo
  103,3,"Dukuyemwo\tabemeye\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri,\tn’ukugira\tibikorwa\tvyiza, n’uguhanurana\tmugukurikiza\rukuri,\rn’uguhanurana\tmugufatana\tmunda\rn’ukwihangana"
  104,1,"Ibihano\tbikaze\tcane\tbizoshikira\tuwurigata\tigikanu\tciwe\tn’ugukwiza insaku"
  104,2,N’uwegeranya amatungo yiwe nukuya harura gusa
  104,3,Mbega yiyumvira yuko amatungo yiwe azoyagumana mu buzima bwiwe bwose
  104,4,Oya! ntankeka uyo muntu azo jugunywa mu muriro udahera witiriwe Huttwamat
  104,5,None n’irihe jambo rizo kumenyesha uwo muriro witiriwe Huttwamat
  104,6,N’umuriro w’Imana wakijwe bimwe bikomeye cane
  104,7,Udugira mu mitima y’abantu
  104,8,Mu vy’ukuri uwo muriro udahera abantu babi bazokwugarirwa mwo babe muriwo
  104,9,Kubishitsi v y’ibiti birebire
  105,1,Mbega ntubona ingene Umuremyi wawe yagize abantu bari bafise inzovu
  105,2,Mbega ntiyagize ingeso zabo zononekara
  105,3,Abarungikira inyoni imirwi n’iyindi
  105,4,Zibatera iminana y’ivyondo vyokeje
  105,5,Zibagira nk’ivyatsi vyariwe
  106,1,Kugira ngo aba Quraishi babandanye
  106,2,Babandanya n’ingendo zabo z’igihe c’imbeho n’igihe c’ubushuhe
  106,3,Rero nibasenge nyene icubahiro ciyi nzu yitiriwe Al’kaabat
  106,4,"Ariwe abarisha mugihe c’inzara, n’ukubaha amahoro mugihe c’ubwoba"
  107,1,Mbega wamubonye umwe ahakana idini ry’Imana
  107,2,Uyo n’umwe asunika impfuvyi
  107,3,Kandi ntiyitaho kugaburira aboro
  107,4,Rero ibihano bikaze cane bizoba shikira abantu basenga
  107,5,Batitaho kumategeko y’amasengesho yabo
  107,6,Abagira ivyo bikorwa vyabo kugira ngo biyereka kubantu gusa
  107,7,Nabo n’abima imfashanyo zabo kubazikeneye
  108,1,Mu vy’ukuri twaguhaye imigisha myinshi cane
  108,2,"Rero n’usenge kubera Umuremyi wawe, kandi ubage kubera Umuremyi wawe"
  108,3,Mu vy’ukuri umwansi wawe niwe azoba imfuvyi
  109,1,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  109,2,Jewe si nsenga ivyo musenga
  109,3,Na mwebwe ntimusenga uwo nsenga
  109,4,Kandi sinzo senga ico musenga
  109,5,Namwe ntimuzo senga uwo nsenga
  109,6,"Mwebwe mufise idini ryanyu, nanje mfise idini ryanje"
  110,1,Nihashika intsinzi y’Imana n’ugutsinda
  110,2,Niwabona abantu binjira mw’idini ry’Imana imirwi n’iyindi
  110,3,"Aho rero nusukure n’Umuremyi wawe hamwe nukuyihayagiza, umusabe ikigongwe, mu vy’ukuri niyo yakira ikigongwe"
  111,1,"Hari\tuguhona\tkw’amaboko\tabiri\tya\tAbuu\tlahhabi,\tnawe\takaba yarahonejwe"
  111,2,"Amatungo yiwe ntaco azo mumarira, canke ivyo yaronkeye ngaha kw’Isi"
  111,3,Azo kwinjira mu muriro udahera waka urubeya runiniya cane
  111,4,N’umukenyezi wiwe yatwara inkwi z’urwanko
  111,5,Mw’izosi ry’iwe hariho umugozi uzinshwe
  112,1,"Vuga uti:- niyo Mana imwe rudende gusa"
  112,2,Imana yonyene gusa niyo ikwiriwe kwizigirwa
  112,3,Ntiyavyaye canke ntiyavutse
  112,4,Kandi ntifise uwo bisa nayo n’umwe
  113,1,"Vuga uti:- ndikinze k’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  113,2,N’ishari yivyo yaremye vyose
  113,3,N’ishari ry’umwijima w’ijoro mugihe ryinjiye
  113,4,N’ishari ry’abahuhera mumafundo
  113,5,N’ishari ry’umufise inzigo mugihe agize iyo nzigo
  114,1,"Vuga uti:- ndikinze ku Muremyi w’abantu bose"
  114,2,Umwami w’abantu bose
  114,3,Asengwa n’abantu bose
  114,4,N’ishari ry’uwushira impungenge n’ugusubira inyuma
  114,5,N’uwushiraho izo mpungenge mu mitima y’abantu
  114,6,Nayo ni mubisigo hamwe n’abantu